00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:04.920 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Trafic et sirènes</c>

00:00:06.400 --> 00:00:09.000 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Voici l'offre alimentaire</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>qui a envahi</c>

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:11.120 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les villes et villages du monde.</c>

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:12.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique électronique douce</c>

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:15.360 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>-Un Français sur deux</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>est en surpoids.</c>

00:00:16.200 --> 00:00:18.240 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Or, les aliments industriels...</c>

00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:20.440 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>-Au sucre, aux graisses, au sel...</c>

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.120 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Sont une bombe sanitaire.</c>

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:24.720 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>-Plats préparés,</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>boissons sucrées sont associés</c>

00:00:25.080 --> 00:00:27.120 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>à un risque accru</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>de 32 problèmes de santé.</c>

00:00:27.480 --> 00:00:28.640 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Sirène</c>

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:32.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-La recherche scientifique</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>a établi des liens</c>

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.680 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>entre aliments industriels</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ultratransformés,</c>

00:00:36.040 --> 00:00:39.000 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et obésité, maladies chroniques</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>et mort prématurée.</c>

00:00:39.920 --> 00:00:40.960 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>-On a montré des liens</c>

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:44.800 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>entre l'exposition aux additifs</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>et aux édulcorants</c>

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:46.920 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>et les risques de pathologies :</c>

00:00:47.280 --> 00:00:49.480 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>cancer, maladie cardiovasculaire</c>
<c.white.bg_black>ou diabète.</c>

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.160 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>-Hypertension, maladie de Crohn,</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>dépression,</c>

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:56.000 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>troubles du sommeil,</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>anxiété et asthme...</c>

00:00:57.040 --> 00:00:59.840 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-On est en crise alimentaire,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>et pourtant,</c>

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:02.720 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>on ne peut s'empêcher</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de consommer ces produits.</c>

00:01:02.920 --> 00:01:04.320 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Pour comprendre, on a interrogé</c>

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:07.080 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>des spécialistes</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'industrie agroalimentaire.</c>

00:01:07.440 --> 00:01:10.280 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:01:10.640 --> 00:01:13.640 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:15.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-On a travaillé pour Heinz,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Cadbury...</c>

00:01:16.280 --> 00:01:17.920 line:79% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Bird's Custard.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-Campbell Soup.</c>

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.480 line:79% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Unilever.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-PepsiCo.</c>

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:21.040 line:79% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Kellogg's.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-Dr Pepper.</c>

00:01:21.400 --> 00:01:23.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:25.280 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Ces experts vont nous expliquer</c>

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:28.880 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>comment les aliments</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ultratransformés ont été inventés,</c>

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:31.640 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>comment les groupes industriels</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>les ont conçus</c>

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:33.880 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour qu'ils soient irrésistibles...</c>

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:38.040 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et comment ils menacent</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>notre santé.</c>

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:39.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de tension</c>

00:01:40.160 --> 00:01:43.640 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:01:48.160 --> 00:01:50.320 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:01:50.520 --> 00:01:54.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:01:55.080 --> 00:01:59.000 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>La nourriture industrielle</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>s'est installée progressivement.</c>

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:01.600 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Si progressivement</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>que pendant longtemps,</c>

00:02:01.960 --> 00:02:05.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>personne n'a remarqué</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>quoi que ce soit d'inquiétant.</c>

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:09.160 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Jusqu'à ce qu'en 2009,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>un scientifique brésilien se penche</c>

00:02:09.520 --> 00:02:10.560 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sur la question.</c>

00:02:10.760 --> 00:02:12.360 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:17.480 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:19.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Je suis Carlos Monteiro,</c>

00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:22.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>professeur de nutrition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et de santé publique</c>

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:24.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>à l'université de São Paulo.</c>

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:27.120 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:02:27.320 --> 00:02:29.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Au départ, nous voulions</c>
<c.green.bg_black>étudier les causes</c>

00:02:30.240 --> 00:02:33.240 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de l'augmentation</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du taux d'obésité au Brésil.</c>

00:02:33.600 --> 00:02:35.120 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:02:35.320 --> 00:02:37.520 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On s'est d'abord intéressés</c>

00:02:40.040 --> 00:02:42.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>aux modifications</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des modes d'alimentation.</c>

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:46.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a constaté que le principal</c>
<c.green.bg_black>changement dans les courses,</c>

00:02:46.360 --> 00:02:47.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>c'était une diminution</c>

00:02:47.800 --> 00:02:49.920 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>drastique des achats</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'huiles de cuisson,</c>

00:02:50.280 --> 00:02:51.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de sucre et de sel.</c>

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:56.680 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ça nous a étonnés,</c>

00:02:56.880 --> 00:03:01.200 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>car ces produits sont considérés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>comme mauvais pour la santé.</c>

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:03.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils provoquent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une prise de poids</c>

00:03:03.320 --> 00:03:06.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et une augmentation</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la masse de graisse.</c>

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:11.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les huiles de cuisson</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ont un Nutri-Score très élevé,</c>

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:12.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>parce qu'elles sont</c>

00:03:12.760 --> 00:03:15.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>composées à 100 %</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de matières grasses.</c>

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais personne ne les consomme</c>

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:21.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>telles quelles, elles sont</c>

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:24.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>utilisées pour cuisiner chez soi.</c>

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:27.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a vu que ces produits</c>

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:29.960 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>avaient été remplacés</c>

00:03:30.320 --> 00:03:32.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>par des nouilles instantanées,</c>

00:03:32.440 --> 00:03:35.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des plats surgelés,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des biscuits, des desserts.</c>

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:39.600 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Aujourd'hui, les gens mangent plus</c>

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:43.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>d'aliments industriels</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que d'aliments préparés à la maison.</c>

00:03:45.480 --> 00:03:46.960 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>C'est le principal changement.</c>

00:03:49.000 --> 00:03:50.160 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Le professeur Monteiro</c>

00:03:50.520 --> 00:03:53.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>a défini une nouvelle</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>classification des aliments.</c>

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.480 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Les produits d'usine,</c>

00:03:54.840 --> 00:03:56.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>prêts à être consommés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ou réchauffés</c>

00:03:57.280 --> 00:04:00.680 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ont été baptisés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>"aliments ultratransformés".</c>

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:02.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:04:02.920 --> 00:04:08.920 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:15.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-La classification NOVA</c>
<c.green.bg_black>n'organise pas les aliments</c>

00:04:15.760 --> 00:04:18.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>en fonction de leur teneur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en éléments nutritifs,</c>

00:04:19.160 --> 00:04:21.200 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>protéines, vitamines ou glucides.</c>

00:04:21.560 --> 00:04:25.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Elle les organise en fonction</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de leur degré de transformation.</c>

00:04:26.120 --> 00:04:28.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:30.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:04:30.280 --> 00:04:31.400 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Le système NOVA</c>

00:04:31.760 --> 00:04:34.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>du professeur classe</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>les aliments en 4 groupes.</c>

00:04:34.720 --> 00:04:37.240 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:40.960 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Dans le système de classification</c>
<c.green.bg_black>NOVA, le groupe 1</c>

00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:43.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>correspond aux aliments frais</c>

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et peu transformés.</c>

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les fruits, les légumes,</c>

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:51.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>les céréales, les légumineuses</c>

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:53.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et la viande.</c>

00:04:53.880 --> 00:04:55.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le groupe 2</c>
<c.green.bg_black>correspond aux ingrédients</c>

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:59.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>utilisés pour cuisiner</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les aliments du groupe 1.</c>

00:05:00.960 --> 00:05:02.480 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Comme le sel, qu'on ajoute</c>

00:05:02.680 --> 00:05:05.840 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour rendre le riz</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et les légumes plus goûteux.</c>

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:07.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Mais c'est aussi</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'huile ou le sucre,</c>

00:05:08.680 --> 00:05:11.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qui sont utilisés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour cuisiner à la maison.</c>

00:05:11.960 --> 00:05:14.600 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:05:14.800 --> 00:05:15.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le groupe 3</c>

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:18.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>est un mélange</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de ces premiers groupes.</c>

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:20.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On y trouve le pain,</c>

00:05:20.520 --> 00:05:21.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le fromage, les condiments,</c>

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>les confitures.</c>

00:05:24.480 --> 00:05:27.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ces 3 premiers groupes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la classification NOVA</c>

00:05:27.560 --> 00:05:29.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>font partie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'un modèle alimentaire sain.</c>

00:05:29.880 --> 00:05:33.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:34.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le groupe 4 est différent.</c>

00:05:35.280 --> 00:05:38.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ce sont les produits industriels</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés,</c>

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:43.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>créés avec des substances extraites</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des aliments et des additifs</c>

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:45.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour les rendre plus attrayants</c>

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:48.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et allonger</c>
<c.green.bg_black>leur durée de conservation.</c>

00:05:48.640 --> 00:05:50.920 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:52.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-On a confirmé que plus</c>

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:56.840 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>les gens mangeaient de produits</c>
<c.green.bg_black>préparés industriellement,</c>

00:05:57.040 --> 00:05:59.720 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>plus le risque d'obésité</c>
<c.green.bg_black>était élevé.</c>

00:06:02.080 --> 00:06:04.280 line:91% align:right
<c.red.bg_black>Mastication au ralenti</c>

00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:06.880 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique calme</c>

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:10.280 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:06:10.640 --> 00:06:13.080 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les nutritionnistes considèrent</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>les graisses,</c>

00:06:13.280 --> 00:06:16.240 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>le sucre et le sel</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>comme des éléments essentiels,</c>

00:06:16.440 --> 00:06:18.040 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>mais en grande quantité,</c>

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:21.760 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ils sont la principale cause</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de problèmes de santé à long terme.</c>

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:23.720 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Pour le professeur Monteiro,</c>

00:06:23.920 --> 00:06:25.600 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>la transformation des aliments</c>

00:06:25.800 --> 00:06:28.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>jouerait un rôle plus important</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>que leur composition</c>

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:30.800 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>dans l'apparition</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>des maladies chroniques.</c>

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:32.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:35.320 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Dix ans plus tard, en 2019,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>aux États-Unis,</c>

00:06:35.680 --> 00:06:38.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>un chercheur</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>remet en question cette hypothèse.</c>

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:42.240 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:06:42.440 --> 00:06:44.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Le concept</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'aliments ultratransformés</c>

00:06:45.200 --> 00:06:47.800 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>part du principe</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les éléments nutritifs</c>

00:06:48.000 --> 00:06:50.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ont un rôle mineur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>par rapport à la transformation.</c>

00:06:51.200 --> 00:06:53.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ça m'a paru un peu fou,</c>

00:06:53.440 --> 00:06:56.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>parce que la nutrition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>s'est toujours concentrée</c>

00:06:56.640 --> 00:06:58.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>sur la composition des aliments.</c>

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:00.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, quand Carlos nous a dit :</c>

00:07:01.120 --> 00:07:04.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"Ça fait des décennies</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que vous faites fausse route",</c>

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:05.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>j'étais assez sceptique.</c>

00:07:06.080 --> 00:07:07.640 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:11.920 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis Kevin Hall, chercheur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à l'Institut national de la santé.</c>

00:07:12.280 --> 00:07:14.320 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:07:14.520 --> 00:07:15.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Pour vérifier</c>

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:19.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>si les aliments ultratransformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sont à l'origine de l'obésité,</c>

00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:21.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on a confié aux diététiciens</c>

00:07:21.800 --> 00:07:24.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de la clinique</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de l'Institut national de la santé</c>

00:07:24.560 --> 00:07:26.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>une mission presque impossible :</c>

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:29.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>concevoir deux régimes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>alimentaires différents.</c>

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:31.880 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:07:32.800 --> 00:07:36.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le premier avec uniquement</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des aliments peu transformés...</c>

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:39.080 line:75% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:07:39.280 --> 00:07:40.320 line:75% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et le second à base</c>

00:07:40.680 --> 00:07:42.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>d'aliments ultratransformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec la même quantité</c>

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:46.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de sel, de sucre, de matières</c>
<c.green.bg_black>grasses, de fibres et de calories.</c>

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.760 line:66% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Il s'agit du premier essai</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>randomisé contrôlé</c>

00:07:51.120 --> 00:07:53.720 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sur les aliments ultratransformés.</c>

00:07:53.920 --> 00:07:55.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Chacun à leur tour,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>20 sujets sont venus</c>

00:07:56.280 --> 00:07:58.360 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>passer un mois à la clinique.</c>

00:07:58.920 --> 00:08:00.400 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Voici votre petit déjeuner.</c>

00:08:00.600 --> 00:08:01.720 line:79%
                    <c.green.bg_black>-Merci, Monica.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-De rien.</c>

00:08:01.920 --> 00:08:03.760 line:79%
                <c.green.bg_black>-Vous êtes un ange.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-Vous avez une heure</c>

00:08:04.120 --> 00:08:05.760 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour manger ce que vous voulez.</c>

00:08:05.960 --> 00:08:07.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-On contrôlait totalement</c>

00:08:07.760 --> 00:08:10.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>leur alimentation</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et on leur servait des repas</c>

00:08:10.440 --> 00:08:11.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>avec des consignes simples :</c>

00:08:12.120 --> 00:08:13.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"Mangez autant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que vous le voulez."</c>

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:15.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais ce qu'ils ignoraient,</c>

00:08:15.880 --> 00:08:18.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>c'est qu'à la fin du repas,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on quantifiait les restes.</c>

00:08:19.760 --> 00:08:22.440 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Je dirais</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il reste 80 % des oeufs.</c>

00:08:22.640 --> 00:08:24.400 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique intrigante</c>

00:08:26.320 --> 00:08:27.840 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Et environ</c>

00:08:28.200 --> 00:08:30.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>5 % des croquettes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de pommes de terre.</c>

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:34.280 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Les diététiciens vont peser le tout.</c>

00:08:34.480 --> 00:08:37.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On connaîtra la quantité exacte</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il a laissée.</c>

00:08:37.520 --> 00:08:38.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:08:39.160 --> 00:08:40.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Tous les jours, on les pesait</c>

00:08:40.960 --> 00:08:43.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et on calculait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les calories brûlées.</c>

00:08:44.040 --> 00:08:47.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, on avait des données</c>
<c.green.bg_black>physiologiques détaillées.</c>

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:49.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mon hypothèse de base était</c>

00:08:49.880 --> 00:08:52.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qu'avec deux régimes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à composition nutritionnelle égale,</c>

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:55.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le nombre de calories consommées</c>
<c.green.bg_black>serait identique.</c>

00:08:56.480 --> 00:08:58.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Évidemment, j'avais tort.</c>

00:08:59.400 --> 00:09:02.240 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-À calories</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>et éléments nutritifs équivalents,</c>

00:09:02.440 --> 00:09:05.360 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les sujets au régime</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ultratransformé prennent du poids,</c>

00:09:05.560 --> 00:09:08.560 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>comme le professeur Monteiro</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>l'a observé au Brésil.</c>

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Il s'est avéré que les sujets</c>

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:13.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>au régime ultratransformé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>consommaient</c>

00:09:14.120 --> 00:09:16.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>systématiquement</c>
<c.green.bg_black>500 calories de plus par jour</c>

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:19.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que ceux qui suivaient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le régime peu transformé.</c>

00:09:20.760 --> 00:09:23.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, ils ont pris du poids</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et de la graisse.</c>

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:27.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a découvert que les aliments</c>

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:28.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés,</c>

00:09:29.080 --> 00:09:31.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>à même composition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en éléments nutritifs,</c>

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:35.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>contenaient beaucoup plus</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de calories par bouchée :</c>

00:09:35.920 --> 00:09:37.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>c'est la densité énergétique.</c>

00:09:38.840 --> 00:09:40.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a aussi constaté</c>

00:09:40.280 --> 00:09:44.200 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il s'agissait souvent d'aliments</c>
<c.green.bg_black>riches en sucre et en gras,</c>

00:09:44.560 --> 00:09:46.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>très rares dans la nature :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on appelle ça</c>

00:09:47.120 --> 00:09:49.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>les aliments hyperappétissants.</c>

00:09:49.840 --> 00:09:51.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:59.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:03.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a proposé aux sujets davantage</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'aliments hyperappétissants</c>

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:06.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>dans le régime ultratransformé,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et ça explique en partie</c>

00:10:07.240 --> 00:10:08.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pourquoi ils ont grossi.</c>

00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:10.560 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:10:10.760 --> 00:10:13.360 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les aliments industriels</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>conditionnés</c>

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:16.240 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>existent depuis les années 1950.</c>

00:10:17.160 --> 00:10:19.880 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais ils se sont généralisés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>dans les années 1970,</c>

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:22.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et l'obésité</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>a commencé à augmenter.</c>

00:10:22.400 --> 00:10:24.760 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:10:25.880 --> 00:10:27.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Je suis Chris van Tulleken,</c>

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:29.960 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>médecin et chercheur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à l'University College</c>

00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:33.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de Londres, en nutrition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et en systèmes alimentaires.</c>

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:36.440 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:10:37.360 --> 00:10:39.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Voici les données</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du gouvernement américain</c>

00:10:39.840 --> 00:10:41.720 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>sur l'obésité masculine</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et féminine.</c>

00:10:41.920 --> 00:10:43.040 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Les courbes correspondent</c>

00:10:43.400 --> 00:10:45.040 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>aux différents groupes d'âge.</c>

00:10:45.240 --> 00:10:46.240 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Entre 1960</c>

00:10:46.600 --> 00:10:50.400 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et 1975, le taux d'obésité</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est resté stable dans la population.</c>

00:10:51.040 --> 00:10:53.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais au milieu des années 70,</c>

00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:56.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>il a commencé à augmenter</c>
<c.green.bg_black>simultanément dans tous les groupes.</c>

00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:00.840 line:75% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a interprété</c>

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:03.240 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>cette hausse de l'obésité</c>
<c.green.bg_black>comme un manque</c>

00:11:03.600 --> 00:11:04.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de volonté.</c>

00:11:04.800 --> 00:11:08.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les gens font de mauvais choix</c>
<c.green.bg_black>par paresse, c'est de leur faute.</c>

00:11:09.160 --> 00:11:12.040 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Mais si l'explication,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>c'est un manque de volonté,</c>

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:15.840 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ça veut dire que ces groupes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>se sont laissés aller en même temps.</c>

00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:18.480 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Et ça, ça ne tient pas la route.</c>

00:11:18.840 --> 00:11:20.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique funk</c>

00:11:21.040 --> 00:11:22.360 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Dans les années 70,</c>

00:11:22.560 --> 00:11:25.400 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les aliments deviennent de plus</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>en plus appétants.</c>

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:26.320 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Un homme va</c>

00:11:26.680 --> 00:11:30.600 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>mettre son diplôme au service</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'industrie agroalimentaire</c>

00:11:30.800 --> 00:11:34.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour fabriquer des produits</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>absolument irrésistibles.</c>

00:11:34.880 --> 00:11:36.560 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Je m'appelle Howard Moskowitz.</c>

00:11:37.400 --> 00:11:39.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis psychologue expérimental.</c>

00:11:40.880 --> 00:11:42.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Certains prétendent que j'ai</c>

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:46.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>révolutionné l'industrie alimentaire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans les années 1970.</c>

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:49.400 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique funk</c>

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:51.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai reçu un appel</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du vice-président</c>

00:11:52.160 --> 00:11:55.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de Campbell Soup qui m'a dit :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>"On est en concurrence</c>

00:11:55.760 --> 00:11:59.320 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>avec une entreprise qui fabrique</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la sauce pour les pâtes."</c>

00:12:00.520 --> 00:12:04.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Cette entreprise utilisait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du concentré de tomates et de l'eau,</c>

00:12:04.360 --> 00:12:06.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>comme le faisait ma mère</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans les années 50.</c>

00:12:07.080 --> 00:12:07.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai dit</c>

00:12:08.240 --> 00:12:09.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>aux gens de Campbell's :</c>

00:12:09.680 --> 00:12:11.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"Vous pouvez faire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mieux qu'eux."</c>

00:12:11.800 --> 00:12:13.680 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ils m'ont demandé comment.</c>

00:12:16.040 --> 00:12:20.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai répondu : "On va chercher</c>
<c.green.bg_black>quels ingrédients associer.</c>

00:12:20.400 --> 00:12:23.720 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On va faire différents mélanges</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et on va les tester."</c>

00:12:24.800 --> 00:12:27.760 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:30.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Au bout du compte,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on a créé 45 produits</c>

00:12:30.800 --> 00:12:33.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et on a demandé à des gens</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de les goûter</c>

00:12:33.640 --> 00:12:34.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et de les évaluer.</c>

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:41.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ça m'a permis de constater</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'en variant systématiquement</c>

00:12:41.360 --> 00:12:43.920 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>les ingrédients</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et qu'en les faisant tester,</c>

00:12:44.120 --> 00:12:46.560 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>on obtenait des résultats limpides.</c>

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:51.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est comme ça qu'est né</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le point de félicité,</c>

00:12:51.880 --> 00:12:53.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qui est le concept</c>
<c.green.bg_black>auquel on m'associe.</c>

00:12:54.640 --> 00:12:57.200 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Plus on ajoute de sucre</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans un produit,</c>

00:12:57.400 --> 00:12:58.600 line:79% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>plus les gens l'aiment,</c>

00:12:58.800 --> 00:13:01.600 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>puis ils se mettent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à l'aimer de moins en moins.</c>

00:13:01.800 --> 00:13:05.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ce point haut, c'est là</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que le produit est le plus apprécié.</c>

00:13:06.560 --> 00:13:07.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est le point de félicité,</c>

00:13:08.280 --> 00:13:09.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le plaisir maximal.</c>

00:13:18.720 --> 00:13:20.920 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ça a été les débuts d'une activité</c>

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:23.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qui a rapporté des milliards</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pendant 30 ans.</c>

00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:26.160 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique funk</c>

00:13:26.520 --> 00:13:28.320 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les industriels</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'agroalimentaire</c>

00:13:28.520 --> 00:13:31.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>cherchent tous le point de félicité</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de leurs produits,</c>

00:13:31.800 --> 00:13:35.840 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et les aliments ultratransformés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>irrésistibles déferlent.</c>

00:13:36.200 --> 00:13:38.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:13:38.400 --> 00:13:40.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Je suis devenu consultant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour des entreprises</c>

00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:46.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>comme Unilever, Pepsi Cola,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Tropicana, Dr Pepper et Spam.</c>

00:13:46.760 --> 00:13:51.760 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:54.560 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Les ventes augmentent toujours</c>

00:13:54.760 --> 00:13:56.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>quand vous vendez</c>
<c.green.bg_black>un produit délicieux</c>

00:13:57.120 --> 00:13:59.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que les gens aiment, c'est simple.</c>

00:13:59.320 --> 00:14:00.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:14:01.520 --> 00:14:05.280 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Dans les années qui suivent</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>la découverte du point de félicité,</c>

00:14:05.640 --> 00:14:07.160 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les aliments sont optimisés.</c>

00:14:07.520 --> 00:14:10.040 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Davantage de sucre et de sel</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>y sont ajoutés,</c>

00:14:10.400 --> 00:14:13.640 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et les consommateurs s'habituent</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>à trouver une vaste gamme</c>

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:16.960 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>de produits pratiques,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>conçus pour être succulents.</c>

00:14:17.320 --> 00:14:18.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique funk</c>

00:14:19.080 --> 00:14:21.160 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>La recherche agroalimentaire</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>explose</c>

00:14:21.360 --> 00:14:24.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et les aliments ultratransformés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>envahissent les rayons</c>

00:14:25.280 --> 00:14:26.600 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>des supermarchés.</c>

00:14:28.760 --> 00:14:33.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Les industriels optimisent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>tous les aspects de leurs produits :</c>

00:14:33.360 --> 00:14:34.400 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>l'arôme, le goût,</c>

00:14:34.760 --> 00:14:36.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>la texture,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour qu'ils soient meilleurs</c>

00:14:37.200 --> 00:14:40.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que ceux de la concurrence</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et qu'ils se vendent mieux.</c>

00:14:42.360 --> 00:14:43.720 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle John Ruff.</c>

00:14:43.920 --> 00:14:46.720 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai travaillé 40 ans</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans l'agroalimentaire,</c>

00:14:46.920 --> 00:14:48.160 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>dans 7 pays différents.</c>

00:14:48.520 --> 00:14:51.000 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mélancolique</c>

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:52.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>En recherche</c>

00:14:52.560 --> 00:14:54.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et développement,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on parlait</c>

00:14:54.640 --> 00:14:56.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de l'entonnoir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du développement produit.</c>

00:14:57.480 --> 00:15:01.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Pour 100 produits qui arrivent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à un stade de développement avancé,</c>

00:15:01.560 --> 00:15:05.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>il en faut 1 000 au début</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour 10 000 idées de départ.</c>

00:15:06.520 --> 00:15:10.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>La plupart des idées ne vont pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>plus loin que l'ébauche papier.</c>

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:12.480 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Mais certaines</c>
<c.green.bg_black>deviennent des prototypes</c>

00:15:12.680 --> 00:15:14.680 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qui vont jusqu'à la phase de test.</c>

00:15:15.640 --> 00:15:18.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Sièges 1 à 14,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>vous allez goûter ces petits cubes.</c>

00:15:20.040 --> 00:15:22.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-On fait appel</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à des panels de goûteurs</c>

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:24.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour fournir des évaluations.</c>

00:15:24.840 --> 00:15:27.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le produit est-il moelleux,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dur, mou, croquant ?</c>

00:15:27.640 --> 00:15:30.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les entreprises agroalimentaires</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sont obligées</c>

00:15:30.680 --> 00:15:33.640 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de fournir aux consommateurs</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ce qu'ils veulent,</c>

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:36.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>sinon,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>elles mettent la clé sous la porte.</c>

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:40.800 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les produits</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>font l'objet de tests complets</c>

00:15:41.000 --> 00:15:42.640 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour déterminer leur point</c>

00:15:43.000 --> 00:15:45.040 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>de félicité</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>qui maximise les ventes.</c>

00:15:45.800 --> 00:15:49.480 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais pour un des scientifiques,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>les questionnaires et les panels</c>

00:15:49.840 --> 00:15:50.920 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sont trop subjectifs.</c>

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:53.240 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Il veut des données précises,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>issues</c>

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:55.000 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'une technologie de pointe.</c>

00:15:58.200 --> 00:15:59.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Parler à un consommateur</c>

00:15:59.560 --> 00:16:02.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ne m'intéresse pas,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>je veux savoir ce qu'il aime</c>

00:16:03.080 --> 00:16:04.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>à un niveau plus profond.</c>

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:05.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On ne sait pas vraiment</c>

00:16:06.240 --> 00:16:07.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pourquoi on aime ce qu'on aime.</c>

00:16:07.840 --> 00:16:10.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais la neuro-imagerie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>permet de comprendre ça.</c>

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:13.880 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique douce au piano</c>

00:16:14.880 --> 00:16:16.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis le professeur McGlone,</c>

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:18.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>neuroscientifique.</c>

00:16:19.920 --> 00:16:22.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai introduit</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'utilisation du scanner</c>

00:16:22.760 --> 00:16:24.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>cérébral chez Unilever.</c>

00:16:26.960 --> 00:16:28.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a mis</c>
<c.green.bg_black>un sujet dans un scanner,</c>

00:16:28.920 --> 00:16:31.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on lui a donné des choses à manger</c>

00:16:31.760 --> 00:16:34.160 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et on a étudié</c>
<c.green.bg_black>son activité cérébrale.</c>

00:16:34.520 --> 00:16:36.400 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:39.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quand on mélange du sucre</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et des matières grasses,</c>

00:16:39.600 --> 00:16:43.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on obtient une substance</c>
<c.green.bg_black>alimentaire très satisfaisante,</c>

00:16:44.080 --> 00:16:45.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>comme la glace au chocolat.</c>

00:16:46.000 --> 00:16:50.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>L'une de nos études consistait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à faire manger différentes glaces</c>

00:16:50.720 --> 00:16:54.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>à des sujets placés dans un scanner.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>On a découvert</c>

00:16:54.560 --> 00:16:57.320 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>que cette zone</c>
<c.green.bg_black>située à l'avant du cerveau,</c>

00:16:57.520 --> 00:17:00.680 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>appelée cortex orbitofrontal</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et qui gère le système</c>

00:17:01.040 --> 00:17:01.760 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>de la récompense,</c>

00:17:02.120 --> 00:17:04.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>brillait de mille feux.</c>

00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:07.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quand on regarde</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'activité du cerveau,</c>

00:17:07.440 --> 00:17:08.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pas de tricherie possible.</c>

00:17:09.080 --> 00:17:10.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>L'imagerie cérébrale</c>

00:17:10.440 --> 00:17:12.480 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>est de plus en plus utilisée</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour prédire</c>

00:17:12.840 --> 00:17:15.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>si les produits auront du succès.</c>

00:17:15.640 --> 00:17:17.400 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique calme</c>

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:24.160 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:17:24.520 --> 00:17:27.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les fabricants de glaces</c>
<c.green.bg_black>s'appuient sur cette imagerie</c>

00:17:28.040 --> 00:17:29.880 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>pour affirmer que leurs produits</c>

00:17:31.360 --> 00:17:34.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>rendent heureux.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Voici l'article qui a été publié</c>

00:17:34.520 --> 00:17:35.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>dans la presse.</c>

00:17:35.720 --> 00:17:38.200 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>"Les glaces activent</c>
<c.white.bg_black>les centres du plaisir"</c>

00:17:39.040 --> 00:17:41.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ça tombe mal,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'article sur l'obésité au-dessus.</c>

00:17:41.800 --> 00:17:43.680 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>"L'obésité accroît</c>
<c.white.bg_black>le risque de démence"</c>

00:17:44.040 --> 00:17:44.800 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Il rit.</c>

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:47.840 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Oui, sacré contraste !</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Vous couperez ça.</c>

00:17:49.840 --> 00:17:53.280 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-En visualisant le point</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de félicité dans le cerveau,</c>

00:17:53.480 --> 00:17:57.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>l'industrie agroalimentaire</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>a pu doser à la perfection le sucre,</c>

00:17:57.400 --> 00:17:59.160 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les matières grasses et le sel,</c>

00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:02.120 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>garantissant ainsi</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>des produits hyperappétents.</c>

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:04.120 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais il y a un problème.</c>

00:18:06.760 --> 00:18:09.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Il est clair</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les aliments ultratransformés</c>

00:18:10.240 --> 00:18:12.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>encouragent la suralimentation.</c>

00:18:12.240 --> 00:18:13.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils sont conçus pour être</c>

00:18:14.080 --> 00:18:18.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>appétissants et que les gens aient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>envie d'en manger toujours plus.</c>

00:18:18.320 --> 00:18:19.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais il y a aussi</c>

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:22.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>leur texture : ils sont élaborés</c>

00:18:22.520 --> 00:18:25.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour être très mous</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et consommés très vite.</c>

00:18:30.800 --> 00:18:33.800 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-On ne pense pas que c'est mou,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>car c'est croquant,</c>

00:18:34.160 --> 00:18:36.560 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>mais passé ce côté croquant,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on l'écrase</c>

00:18:36.920 --> 00:18:39.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>avec la langue,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>il n'a aucune consistance.</c>

00:18:41.360 --> 00:18:44.360 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Le gâteau apéritif croustille.</c>

00:18:44.560 --> 00:18:45.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Fini.</c>

00:18:46.280 --> 00:18:48.040 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>En termes de calories par gramme,</c>

00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:51.440 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>c'est bien plus calorique</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'un hamburger gras.</c>

00:18:52.520 --> 00:18:55.040 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>La texture</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et la densité énergétique</c>

00:18:55.240 --> 00:18:57.400 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>font que ça se mange très vite.</c>

00:18:58.680 --> 00:19:00.520 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>L'agroalimentaire a un terme</c>

00:19:00.720 --> 00:19:04.240 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>pour ces aliments légers</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui fondent dans la bouche :</c>

00:19:04.600 --> 00:19:07.360 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>on parle</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de "densité calorique évanescente".</c>

00:19:07.560 --> 00:19:09.480 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique intrigante</c>

00:19:09.840 --> 00:19:19.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:19:20.040 --> 00:19:23.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Le nombre élevé de calories</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>par bouchée est un élément clé</c>

00:19:23.880 --> 00:19:26.800 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>qui étaye l'hypothèse</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>selon laquelle les aliments</c>

00:19:27.160 --> 00:19:30.080 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ultratransformés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>poussent les gens à trop manger.</c>

00:19:30.440 --> 00:19:33.840 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Les spécialistes de Tastehead</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>vont nous expliquer pourquoi.</c>

00:19:34.040 --> 00:19:36.160 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique intrigante</c>

00:19:36.520 --> 00:19:38.560 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:19:38.920 --> 00:19:40.120 line:91% align:right
<c.red.bg_black>Le fouet racle le bol.</c>

00:19:41.680 --> 00:19:42.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Chez Tastehead,</c>

00:19:42.880 --> 00:19:45.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on développe aliments et boissons</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour les fabricants.</c>

00:19:46.040 --> 00:19:48.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a travaillé pour Heinz,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Cadbury, Pringles.</c>

00:19:48.760 --> 00:19:50.120 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique intrigante</c>

00:19:50.320 --> 00:19:52.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Prenons l'exemple</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de ce friand industriel,</c>

00:19:53.120 --> 00:19:56.480 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>version ultratransformée</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'une tourte à la viande maison.</c>

00:19:56.680 --> 00:19:59.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:19:59.440 --> 00:20:02.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Ce friand contient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>environ 500 calories.</c>

00:20:03.440 --> 00:20:04.960 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>C'est un mélange de glucides,</c>

00:20:05.320 --> 00:20:06.640 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de matières grasses</c>

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:08.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et de protéines.</c>

00:20:08.320 --> 00:20:10.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais sa méthode de fabrication fait</c>

00:20:10.600 --> 00:20:12.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il a</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une forte densité énergétique.</c>

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:15.120 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Parce qu'il est riche en gras.</c>

00:20:16.080 --> 00:20:19.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Et tout ce gras</c>
<c.green.bg_black>donne un produit très mou.</c>

00:20:19.360 --> 00:20:21.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique intrigante</c>

00:20:22.040 --> 00:20:24.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ce que les gens ne savent pas,</c>

00:20:24.480 --> 00:20:28.080 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>c'est que l'ultratransformation</c>
<c.green.bg_black>modifie les textures</c>

00:20:28.440 --> 00:20:31.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des aliments,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ça les rend beaucoup plus tendres.</c>

00:20:31.840 --> 00:20:33.640 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:20:33.840 --> 00:20:35.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Voici une salade simple</c>

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:37.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>composée de poulet,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>riz brun et avocat.</c>

00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:41.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Sa quantité de matières grasses,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de protéines</c>

00:20:41.760 --> 00:20:44.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et de glucides</c>
<c.green.bg_black>correspond à celle du friand.</c>

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:48.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>À 500 calories, leur composition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>nutritionnelle est identique.</c>

00:20:48.680 --> 00:20:50.360 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:20:51.000 --> 00:20:53.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Faisons un petit jeu :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>tu prends la salade,</c>

00:20:54.120 --> 00:20:55.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>moi, le friand.</c>

00:20:55.200 --> 00:20:57.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Voyons combien de temps</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on met à les manger.</c>

00:20:57.800 --> 00:20:59.600 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique intrigante</c>

00:20:59.800 --> 00:21:01.880 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:21:02.240 --> 00:21:04.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:06.760 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-La perception de la texture</c>

00:21:07.120 --> 00:21:09.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>contribue à la façon de manger.</c>

00:21:10.480 --> 00:21:12.120 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Les aliments qu'il faut mâcher</c>

00:21:12.480 --> 00:21:13.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>demandent un effort.</c>

00:21:13.800 --> 00:21:16.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Cet effort prend du temps,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>c'est l'avantage,</c>

00:21:16.640 --> 00:21:18.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ce qui n'est pas le cas</c>

00:21:18.400 --> 00:21:19.680 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>pour les aliments mous.</c>

00:21:22.920 --> 00:21:25.040 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Le riz brun</c>
<c.green.bg_black>demande de la mastication.</c>

00:21:25.240 --> 00:21:27.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:21:27.880 --> 00:21:29.520 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-La faim et la satiété,</c>

00:21:29.880 --> 00:21:31.240 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>le sentiment d'être rassasié,</c>

00:21:31.440 --> 00:21:34.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sont régulées par des mécanismes</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de réponse complexes.</c>

00:21:34.800 --> 00:21:37.800 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Des capteurs d'étirement</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>dans la paroi de l'estomac</c>

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:40.000 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>envoient au cerveau</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>des signaux indiquant</c>

00:21:40.360 --> 00:21:42.560 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>que l'estomac</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>est en train de se dilater.</c>

00:21:43.240 --> 00:21:45.120 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Le niveau de ghréline,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>l'hormone de la faim,</c>

00:21:45.480 --> 00:21:48.120 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>diminue à mesure que l'estomac</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>se remplit.</c>

00:21:48.840 --> 00:21:51.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais ça demande du temps :</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>il faut 20 min</c>

00:21:51.560 --> 00:21:53.160 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour que ces signaux parviennent</c>

00:21:53.520 --> 00:21:56.640 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>au cerveau et que la sensation</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de faim disparaisse.</c>

00:21:59.880 --> 00:22:02.480 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-J'ai mis plus de temps</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à manger la salade.</c>

00:22:02.680 --> 00:22:04.520 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Le friand s'avale très vite.</c>

00:22:06.040 --> 00:22:09.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Là, on court-circuite</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des mécanismes naturels</c>

00:22:09.240 --> 00:22:11.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qui limitent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la quantité de calories</c>

00:22:12.160 --> 00:22:14.280 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qu'on peut intégrer en peu de temps.</c>

00:22:14.920 --> 00:22:16.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Qui aura faim en premier ?</c>

00:22:16.840 --> 00:22:18.560 line:79%
                              <c.green.bg_black>-Toi.</c>
          <c.green.bg_black>-Absolument.</c>

00:22:18.760 --> 00:22:21.000 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Toutes ces fibres ingérées</c>
<c.green.bg_black>vont me rassasier</c>

00:22:21.360 --> 00:22:22.880 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>plus longtemps.</c>

00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:24.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:22:25.080 --> 00:22:26.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:22:26.280 --> 00:22:29.520 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-On mange ces aliments</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés si vite</c>

00:22:29.920 --> 00:22:34.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>que le corps n'a pas le temps</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'apprécier la quantité ingérée.</c>

00:22:35.320 --> 00:22:38.840 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ils sont conçus essentiellement</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour passer outre</c>

00:22:39.040 --> 00:22:42.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>notre capacité à réguler</c>
<c.green.bg_black>notre apport énergétique.</c>

00:22:43.920 --> 00:22:46.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Donc,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ils incitent à la suralimentation.</c>

00:22:48.160 --> 00:22:50.520 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:22:50.720 --> 00:22:53.680 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Le taux d'obésité</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>augmente partout. En Europe,</c>

00:22:54.040 --> 00:22:57.560 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>près de la moitié de la population</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>adulte est en surpoids.</c>

00:22:57.760 --> 00:23:05.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:23:05.440 --> 00:23:07.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-L'enfer est pavé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de bonnes intentions.</c>

00:23:10.080 --> 00:23:11.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a créé ces produits</c>

00:23:11.680 --> 00:23:14.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>parce qu'ils vont</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans le sens de l'évolution.</c>

00:23:16.040 --> 00:23:20.200 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On ne vend pas de la sauce tomate,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la sauce pour pâtes,</c>

00:23:20.400 --> 00:23:22.600 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>des cornichons, du Tropicana...</c>

00:23:23.440 --> 00:23:25.200 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On vend de la satisfaction,</c>

00:23:25.400 --> 00:23:27.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de la promotion sociale</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et des emplois.</c>

00:23:28.720 --> 00:23:30.400 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:23:30.600 --> 00:23:39.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:23:39.240 --> 00:23:41.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Lorsque les plats préparés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>apparaissent,</c>

00:23:42.120 --> 00:23:45.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>personne n'est mieux placé</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>que les fabricants de cigarettes</c>

00:23:46.280 --> 00:23:47.560 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour vendre du plaisir.</c>

00:23:49.200 --> 00:23:51.280 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Certains grands groupes</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>agroalimentaires</c>

00:23:51.480 --> 00:23:54.600 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>s'inspirent du marketing</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>des fabricants de tabac.</c>

00:23:57.680 --> 00:24:00.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Je m'intéressais</c>
<c.green.bg_black>aux aliments ultratransformés</c>

00:24:01.120 --> 00:24:03.240 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>quand un de mes collègues m'a dit :</c>

00:24:03.440 --> 00:24:05.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>"J'ai fouillé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans les archives des fabricants</c>

00:24:06.120 --> 00:24:09.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de tabac et tu devrais</c>
<c.green.bg_black>jeter un oeil à leurs documents."</c>

00:24:09.800 --> 00:24:11.560 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:24:11.920 --> 00:24:13.560 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:24:13.760 --> 00:24:16.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Il s'est avéré que leurs archives</c>

00:24:16.800 --> 00:24:19.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>contenaient des centaines</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de milliers de documents</c>

00:24:19.720 --> 00:24:22.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>sur des entreprises</c>
<c.green.bg_black>agroalimentaires.</c>

00:24:22.600 --> 00:24:25.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis Laura Schmidt,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>professeure à la fac de médecine</c>

00:24:25.960 --> 00:24:28.200 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de l'université de San Francisco.</c>

00:24:28.560 --> 00:24:30.280 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:24:30.480 --> 00:24:32.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:24:33.320 --> 00:24:36.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>À partir des années 1960,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le cigarettier R. J. Reynolds</c>

00:24:36.840 --> 00:24:39.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>a commencé à racheter</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des entreprises alimentaires.</c>

00:24:39.840 --> 00:24:41.320 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:24:41.520 --> 00:24:44.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Pourquoi un géant du tabac</c>
<c.green.bg_black>rachèterait-il</c>

00:24:44.400 --> 00:24:46.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des entreprises alimentaires ?</c>

00:24:48.440 --> 00:24:50.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a été surpris de découvrir</c>

00:24:50.560 --> 00:24:53.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que les industriels du tabac</c>
<c.green.bg_black>fabriquaient</c>

00:24:53.520 --> 00:24:58.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>en laboratoire un grand nombre</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de colorants et d'arômes artificiels</c>

00:24:58.360 --> 00:25:00.400 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour les ajouter aux cigarettes,</c>

00:25:01.920 --> 00:25:04.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des arômes comme le menthol.</c>

00:25:05.720 --> 00:25:09.200 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Leurs laboratoires fabriquaient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ces substances pour les ajouter</c>

00:25:09.560 --> 00:25:11.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>aux cigarettes et créer</c>

00:25:11.240 --> 00:25:13.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des produits destinés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à de nouveaux fumeurs.</c>

00:25:14.000 --> 00:25:15.200 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ce sont "des extensions</c>

00:25:15.560 --> 00:25:16.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de gamme".</c>

00:25:24.840 --> 00:25:27.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique entraînante</c>

00:25:28.160 --> 00:25:30.440 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:25:30.640 --> 00:25:33.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Des Virginia Slims</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour celles voulant être minces.</c>

00:25:33.480 --> 00:25:37.080 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Des Marlboro pour les hommes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ne décollant pas de leur canapé,</c>

00:25:37.280 --> 00:25:39.640 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>mais qui rêvent d'être des cow-boys.</c>

00:25:40.080 --> 00:25:43.280 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>-Je vais vous raconter l'histoire</c>

00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:46.240 line:75% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>de la marque Marlboro...</c>

00:25:48.360 --> 00:25:49.560 line:79% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ils ciblaient les enfants</c>

00:25:49.920 --> 00:25:52.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>avec des personnages</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de dessins animés.</c>

00:25:52.560 --> 00:25:55.520 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:25:56.920 --> 00:25:59.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Joe Camel était</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'un de ces personnages.</c>

00:25:59.320 --> 00:26:01.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>R. J. Reynolds</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'a mis sur ses paquets,</c>

00:26:01.600 --> 00:26:05.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>car l'entreprise tenait à faire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>connaître la marque aux enfants</c>

00:26:06.080 --> 00:26:08.560 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour que plus tard,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ils fument des Camel.</c>

00:26:08.920 --> 00:26:11.280 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Une enquête a révélé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les enfants de 6 ans</c>

00:26:11.640 --> 00:26:14.680 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>connaissaient Joe Camel</c>
<c.green.bg_black>aussi bien que Mickey Mouse.</c>

00:26:16.600 --> 00:26:18.880 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-La stratégie</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'industrie du tabac</c>

00:26:19.240 --> 00:26:21.080 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>a consisté à rendre attrayant</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>un produit</c>

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:23.480 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>à l'apparence neutre</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>à grand renfort</c>

00:26:23.840 --> 00:26:25.960 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>de couleurs, d'arômes, de marketing</c>

00:26:26.160 --> 00:26:29.880 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et de personnages de dessins animés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour cibler différents marchés.</c>

00:26:31.800 --> 00:26:32.800 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Dans ces archives,</c>

00:26:33.160 --> 00:26:35.680 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>L. Schmidt a découvert</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>que les fabricants de tabac</c>

00:26:35.880 --> 00:26:38.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>comptaient utiliser</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ces stratégies marketing</c>

00:26:38.400 --> 00:26:40.120 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour vendre de la nourriture.</c>

00:26:42.360 --> 00:26:43.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-On a trouvé</c>

00:26:43.440 --> 00:26:44.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>cette note rédigée en 1962</c>

00:26:45.040 --> 00:26:47.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>par le laboratoire de R. J. Reynolds</c>

00:26:47.800 --> 00:26:49.440 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et adressée au PDG</c>

00:26:49.800 --> 00:26:50.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de l'entreprise.</c>

00:26:51.000 --> 00:26:53.480 line:66% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>"PROPOSITION DE DIVERSIFICATION</c>
<c.white.bg_black>PRODUCTION D'ARÔMES"</c>

00:26:53.840 --> 00:26:56.000 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Il dit :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>"Pour des raisons de commodité,</c>

00:26:56.360 --> 00:26:59.960 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on qualifie R. J. Reynolds</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de fabricant de tabac.</c>

00:27:03.600 --> 00:27:06.200 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Cependant, R. J. Reynolds</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est plus largement</c>

00:27:06.560 --> 00:27:08.240 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>un fabricant de saveurs."</c>

00:27:13.440 --> 00:27:14.720 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ensuite, il parle</c>

00:27:15.080 --> 00:27:16.440 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>d'une fusion avec une société,</c>

00:27:17.280 --> 00:27:19.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Pacific Hawaiian Products Company.</c>

00:27:20.040 --> 00:27:21.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique hawaïenne</c>

00:27:22.080 --> 00:27:24.240 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:27:24.440 --> 00:27:27.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Qui fabrique une seule chose :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une boisson aux fruits.</c>

00:27:27.640 --> 00:27:30.880 line:79% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:27:32.000 --> 00:27:36.240 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le Hawaiian Punch existait en une</c>
<c.green.bg_black>seule saveur et une seule couleur.</c>

00:27:36.440 --> 00:27:38.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'était une boisson rouge vif</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour adultes.</c>

00:27:40.000 --> 00:27:41.440 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Mais en quelques années,</c>

00:27:41.640 --> 00:27:44.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ils l'ont transformée</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en une boisson pour enfants.</c>

00:27:45.040 --> 00:27:46.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Un petit coup de punch ?</c>

00:27:46.880 --> 00:27:47.880 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-D'accord !</c>

00:27:51.080 --> 00:27:53.240 line:83% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>-Qu'est-ce qui donne</c>
<c.magenta.bg_black>au Hawaiian Punch</c>

00:27:53.920 --> 00:27:55.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>son punch ?</c>

00:27:56.320 --> 00:27:59.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ils ont eu l'intuition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il fallait cibler les enfants</c>

00:28:00.280 --> 00:28:03.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>parce qu'ils deviendraient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des consommateurs à vie.</c>

00:28:04.520 --> 00:28:07.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ce qui est brillant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec leur stratégie marketing,</c>

00:28:07.480 --> 00:28:10.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>c'est qu'on peut prendre</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le modèle utilisé pour le tabac</c>

00:28:10.600 --> 00:28:13.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et l'appliquer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à l'industrie agroalimentaire.</c>

00:28:13.720 --> 00:28:16.440 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:28:17.920 --> 00:28:21.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On peut créer une multitude</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'extensions de gamme...</c>

00:28:23.960 --> 00:28:27.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>avec des campagnes publicitaires</c>
<c.green.bg_black>élaborées qui entrent</c>

00:28:27.400 --> 00:28:28.840 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>dans la tête des consommateurs</c>

00:28:29.040 --> 00:28:31.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour leur donner envie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de vos produits.</c>

00:28:36.520 --> 00:28:38.240 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les entreprises</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'agroalimentaire</c>

00:28:38.440 --> 00:28:41.320 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>conçoivent des aliments</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ultratransformés attrayants</c>

00:28:41.680 --> 00:28:44.320 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>qu'elles rendent exprès</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>faciles et rapides à manger.</c>

00:28:44.520 --> 00:28:45.960 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Pour les vendre, elles utilisent</c>

00:28:46.160 --> 00:28:48.240 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>des techniques</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de marketing irrésistibles.</c>

00:28:50.360 --> 00:28:52.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Et elles ne sont jamais</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>à court d'idées</c>

00:28:52.400 --> 00:28:53.640 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour nous tenter.</c>

00:28:56.680 --> 00:28:59.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Manger est une expérience</c>
<c.green.bg_black>multisensorielle.</c>

00:29:00.080 --> 00:29:02.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Il y a l'aspect de la nourriture,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>son odeur,</c>

00:29:03.720 --> 00:29:04.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>la sensation</c>

00:29:05.080 --> 00:29:06.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qu'elle provoque sur les doigts...</c>

00:29:07.880 --> 00:29:09.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Même le son est important.</c>

00:29:13.760 --> 00:29:17.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'intéresse aux préférences</c>
<c.green.bg_black>alimentaires et aux mécanismes</c>

00:29:17.520 --> 00:29:19.760 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>sensoriels qui les sous-tendent.</c>

00:29:22.040 --> 00:29:25.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle Barry Smith.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis philosophe et travaille</c>

00:29:25.480 --> 00:29:26.720 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>sur les analyses sensorielles</c>

00:29:26.920 --> 00:29:29.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>avec des neuroscientifiques</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et psychologues.</c>

00:29:29.560 --> 00:29:31.040 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Froissement</c>

00:29:31.400 --> 00:29:32.080 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Craquement</c>

00:29:35.120 --> 00:29:38.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Quand on ouvre une canette de soda,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on entend 2 sons :</c>

00:29:38.840 --> 00:29:41.480 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>le clic et l'ouverture.</c>

00:29:41.840 --> 00:29:43.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les ingénieurs du son</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et les fabricants</c>

00:29:44.000 --> 00:29:46.840 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>travaillent dur pour obtenir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le son parfait.</c>

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:48.640 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>C'est l'identité sonore.</c>

00:30:03.560 --> 00:30:05.040 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Nombre d'entreprises voulaient</c>

00:30:05.240 --> 00:30:07.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>que je travaille</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur leur identité sonore.</c>

00:30:07.400 --> 00:30:09.880 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Les gens de Kellogg's</c>
<c.green.bg_black>m'ont demandé :</c>

00:30:10.600 --> 00:30:12.440 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>"C'est quoi, l'identité sonore ?"</c>

00:30:12.640 --> 00:30:15.360 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai répondu : "C'est vous</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui l'avez inventée !"</c>

00:30:18.720 --> 00:30:20.920 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Beaucoup de gens se souviennent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que, petits,</c>

00:30:21.120 --> 00:30:22.880 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ils portaient leur bol</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à leur oreille.</c>

00:30:23.080 --> 00:30:24.200 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Pour écouter quoi ?</c>

00:30:25.680 --> 00:30:26.680 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Le crépitement</c>

00:30:27.040 --> 00:30:28.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des céréales.</c>

00:30:28.360 --> 00:30:30.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Meilleur exemple d'identité sonore.</c>

00:30:33.080 --> 00:30:34.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>-Mets des Snap, Crackle et Pop</c>

00:30:35.040 --> 00:30:37.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>dans ton petit déjeuner !</c>

00:30:38.600 --> 00:30:41.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les Pringles</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sont souvent irrésistibles.</c>

00:30:41.600 --> 00:30:44.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Leur slogan le dit :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>"C'est une explosion de saveurs."</c>

00:30:47.640 --> 00:30:48.920 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>-Des chips dans un tube !</c>

00:30:49.280 --> 00:30:50.680 line:75% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Une explosion de saveurs !</c>

00:30:51.040 --> 00:30:52.040 line:75% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Quand on a commencé,</c>

00:30:52.400 --> 00:30:53.960 line:75% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>on ne peut plus s'arrêter !</c>

00:30:57.840 --> 00:31:00.880 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les odeurs et les sons</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>nous évoquent des souvenirs</c>

00:31:01.080 --> 00:31:03.320 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et nous donnent envie</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'un aliment bien avant</c>

00:31:03.680 --> 00:31:04.760 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'avoir en bouche.</c>

00:31:08.640 --> 00:31:11.040 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>En plus de jouer</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>sur l'identité sonore,</c>

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:12.520 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les industriels font appel</c>

00:31:12.880 --> 00:31:14.680 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>à des spécialistes pour exploiter</c>

00:31:14.880 --> 00:31:18.120 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>nos comportements alimentaires</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>les plus profondément ancrés.</c>

00:31:22.240 --> 00:31:25.120 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Chez Pringles,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'entreprise était préoccupée</c>

00:31:25.320 --> 00:31:28.040 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>par la concurrence de Doritos</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et voulait innover.</c>

00:31:29.720 --> 00:31:32.440 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>L'une des idées proposées</c>
<c.green.bg_black>était d'agrandir le tube</c>

00:31:32.640 --> 00:31:34.240 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>pour pouvoir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>y mettre la main.</c>

00:31:35.440 --> 00:31:38.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Mais j'ai dit :</c>
<c.green.bg_black>"Non, non, non, surtout pas.</c>

00:31:38.560 --> 00:31:41.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les gens adorent essayer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de mettre la main à l'intérieur.</c>

00:31:42.040 --> 00:31:44.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils sont comme des ours</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en quête de nourriture,</c>

00:31:44.720 --> 00:31:48.280 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et essayer de l'attraper,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ça augmente leur désir de manger."</c>

00:31:51.440 --> 00:31:53.600 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Le plaisir de manger est analysé</c>

00:31:53.960 --> 00:31:56.280 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et hyper optimisé,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>car plus on aime,</c>

00:31:57.000 --> 00:31:58.080 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>plus on achète.</c>

00:31:59.640 --> 00:32:00.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Ça sent très fort.</c>

00:32:04.320 --> 00:32:07.360 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les fabricants changent</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>nos habitudes alimentaires</c>

00:32:07.720 --> 00:32:10.480 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>en nous incitant</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>à grignoter continuellement.</c>

00:32:13.960 --> 00:32:14.960 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Jolie couleur.</c>

00:32:15.160 --> 00:32:17.480 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Le grignotage est devenu la norme.</c>

00:32:22.080 --> 00:32:23.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ah merde !</c>

00:32:30.800 --> 00:32:33.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-J'étais ingénieure agroalimentaire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>au Mexique.</c>

00:32:34.200 --> 00:32:35.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai travaillé pour Cargill.</c>

00:32:39.360 --> 00:32:41.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Cette entreprise produit</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les ingrédients bruts</c>

00:32:41.880 --> 00:32:44.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>présents</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans les aliments transformés.</c>

00:32:44.600 --> 00:32:46.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>La farine, le sucre, l'huile,</c>

00:32:46.560 --> 00:32:49.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le sirop de maïs</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à haute teneur en fructose</c>

00:32:49.480 --> 00:32:50.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et le cacao.</c>

00:32:54.800 --> 00:32:57.960 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ces dernières années, au Mexique,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>j'ai remarqué un afflux</c>

00:32:58.320 --> 00:33:01.200 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de produits conditionnés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>venus des États-Unis.</c>

00:33:02.240 --> 00:33:04.840 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai commencé à voir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les Mexicains grossir</c>

00:33:05.040 --> 00:33:08.080 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et à entendre parler de maladies</c>
<c.green.bg_black>comme le diabète de type 2</c>

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:10.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ou le cancer chez les jeunes.</c>

00:33:12.640 --> 00:33:16.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quel était l'impact de mon employeur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur la santé du pays ?</c>

00:33:16.640 --> 00:33:17.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai décidé de changer</c>

00:33:18.120 --> 00:33:20.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de métier pour faire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la santé publique.</c>

00:33:21.000 --> 00:33:22.320 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Propos en anglais</c>

00:33:22.680 --> 00:33:24.800 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique de suspense</c>

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:27.440 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle Yanaina Chavez-Ugalde.</c>

00:33:27.640 --> 00:33:29.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis chercheuse</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à l'université de Cambridge</c>

00:33:30.320 --> 00:33:32.320 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et je connais très bien</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le fonctionnement</c>

00:33:32.520 --> 00:33:35.640 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>des entreprises agroalimentaires</c>
<c.green.bg_black>puisque j'y ai travaillé.</c>

00:33:38.880 --> 00:33:40.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>La concurrence est féroce.</c>

00:33:41.640 --> 00:33:44.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>L'argent dépend de la quantité</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de produits consommés.</c>

00:33:44.920 --> 00:33:48.200 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, les entreprises se battent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour leur part d'estomac.</c>

00:33:48.560 --> 00:33:56.480 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:33:57.400 --> 00:33:59.480 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>C'est la course à la part d'estomac.</c>

00:33:59.840 --> 00:34:01.720 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Comme il y a plusieurs heures</c>

00:34:01.920 --> 00:34:04.360 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>entre le petit déjeuner,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le déjeuner et le dîner,</c>

00:34:05.720 --> 00:34:08.240 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>les fabricants veulent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'on grignote.</c>

00:34:08.600 --> 00:34:12.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:34:13.320 --> 00:34:15.920 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On se réveille,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>1er encas de la journée :</c>

00:34:16.280 --> 00:34:19.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>une boisson pour le petit déjeuner</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformée.</c>

00:34:19.520 --> 00:34:22.600 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Hyper marketée,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>elle est à consommer sans s'asseoir,</c>

00:34:22.800 --> 00:34:25.080 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>sans prendre le temps</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de manger quelque chose.</c>

00:34:26.520 --> 00:34:28.480 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Deuxième encas de la journée.</c>

00:34:30.640 --> 00:34:33.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Des calories vides,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>riches en énergie,</c>

00:34:33.680 --> 00:34:36.440 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pauvres en nutriments.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Mi-journée, petit creux,</c>

00:34:36.800 --> 00:34:38.520 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>donc, on nous propose quoi ?</c>

00:34:39.320 --> 00:34:40.840 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Des gressins de légumes.</c>

00:34:41.800 --> 00:34:43.800 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Voilà un bon exemple d'encas</c>

00:34:44.160 --> 00:34:46.080 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>avec une allégation de santé.</c>

00:34:46.280 --> 00:34:48.640 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Avant, on aurait mangé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>un aliment naturel.</c>

00:34:49.000 --> 00:34:52.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Là, on nous fait croire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que c'est un substitut sain.</c>

00:34:54.640 --> 00:34:57.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Certains encas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sont conçus pour être associés</c>

00:34:57.240 --> 00:35:00.120 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>à un comportement sain</c>
<c.green.bg_black>comme l'activité physique.</c>

00:35:00.480 --> 00:35:03.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Après avoir fait du sport,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>je mange une barre</c>

00:35:04.120 --> 00:35:05.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>hyperprotéinée, pauvre en sucres.</c>

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:09.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ose même pas l'ouvrir.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Je veux pas y toucher.</c>

00:35:09.880 --> 00:35:10.640 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Pourquoi ?</c>

00:35:11.000 --> 00:35:12.960 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-C'est une formulation industrielle.</c>

00:35:16.160 --> 00:35:17.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Une fois qu'on a fini</c>

00:35:17.680 --> 00:35:18.840 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de dîner, on a ces encas</c>

00:35:19.200 --> 00:35:21.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>vendus comme étant à partager.</c>

00:35:21.400 --> 00:35:22.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>En fait, on les mange seuls</c>

00:35:23.120 --> 00:35:24.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>devant sa télé.</c>

00:35:25.680 --> 00:35:26.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'adore ça !</c>

00:35:27.120 --> 00:35:28.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je peux pas m'arrêter</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'en manger.</c>

00:35:30.640 --> 00:35:31.800 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Rires</c>

00:35:32.000 --> 00:35:33.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est compulsif !</c>

00:35:34.400 --> 00:35:35.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Oh non...</c>

00:35:35.920 --> 00:35:37.080 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>...</c>

00:35:37.440 --> 00:35:39.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:35:39.400 --> 00:35:41.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:35:41.240 --> 00:35:42.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-L'idée qu'on aurait</c>

00:35:42.600 --> 00:35:44.600 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>besoin d'un produit</c>
<c.green.bg_black>spécialement conçu</c>

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.760 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>en milieu de matinée</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ou d'après-midi,</c>

00:35:46.960 --> 00:35:50.120 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>avant ou après avoir couru,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est aberrante.</c>

00:35:51.720 --> 00:35:53.760 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Aucun encas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>n'est meilleur pour la santé</c>

00:35:53.960 --> 00:35:56.080 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>qu'une poignée de noix,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une banane,</c>

00:35:56.280 --> 00:35:58.320 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>un verre de lait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ou un morceau de pain.</c>

00:35:58.520 --> 00:36:00.200 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Propos en anglais</c>

00:36:00.560 --> 00:36:01.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Aucun.</c>

00:36:03.160 --> 00:36:06.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les athlètes ne consomment pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ces produits industriels.</c>

00:36:06.880 --> 00:36:08.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils mangent de vrais aliments.</c>

00:36:09.720 --> 00:36:10.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Il a été prouvé</c>

00:36:11.080 --> 00:36:13.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que c'est</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ce qui est bon pour nous.</c>

00:36:14.160 --> 00:36:17.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le corps a évolué en mangeant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la vraie nourriture,</c>

00:36:17.200 --> 00:36:20.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pas des glucides modifiés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec des isolats de protéines,</c>

00:36:20.840 --> 00:36:23.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des graisses raffinées,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>blanchies et désodorisées,</c>

00:36:23.880 --> 00:36:25.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le tout émulsionné et aromatisé.</c>

00:36:26.160 --> 00:36:28.360 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:36:29.640 --> 00:36:31.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les industriels</c>
<c.green.bg_black>veulent seulement</c>

00:36:31.560 --> 00:36:33.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>vous soutirer de l'argent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à toute heure</c>

00:36:34.120 --> 00:36:35.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de la journée.</c>

00:36:35.320 --> 00:36:38.520 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:36:38.880 --> 00:36:42.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ces produits pleins de sucre,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de sel ou de graisses saturées,</c>

00:36:44.160 --> 00:36:45.320 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ces "aliments",</c>

00:36:45.520 --> 00:36:47.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>c'est pas de la nourriture,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>bon sang !</c>

00:36:48.680 --> 00:36:50.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Désolée, c'est...</c>

00:36:52.040 --> 00:36:53.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est des formulations</c>

00:36:54.320 --> 00:36:57.320 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>dont le but est de générer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>toujours plus de profit.</c>

00:36:57.680 --> 00:37:00.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:37:00.240 --> 00:37:02.760 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les aliments ultratransformés</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>bouleversent</c>

00:37:03.120 --> 00:37:05.320 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les habitudes alimentaires partout.</c>

00:37:05.680 --> 00:37:08.040 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Dans les zones rurales</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>du nord de la Colombie,</c>

00:37:08.240 --> 00:37:10.600 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les produits</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>gras et sucrés supplantent</c>

00:37:10.800 --> 00:37:12.800 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>le mode d'alimentation traditionnel</c>

00:37:13.160 --> 00:37:15.280 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>avec de graves répercussions</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>sur la santé.</c>

00:37:15.480 --> 00:37:19.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:37:20.960 --> 00:37:23.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ça fait plusieurs fois</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que je me rends à La Guajira</c>

00:37:24.200 --> 00:37:27.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour essayer de comprendre</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la crise alimentaire de la région.</c>

00:37:27.720 --> 00:37:29.680 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:37:30.800 --> 00:37:33.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Válerin Saurith López.</c>

00:37:33.600 --> 00:37:36.240 line:50% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis nutritionniste</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et chercheuse.</c>

00:37:38.120 --> 00:37:39.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Depuis six ans,</c>

00:37:39.680 --> 00:37:42.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on a vu</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les aliments ultratransformés</c>

00:37:42.800 --> 00:37:44.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>avaient remplacé le régime</c>

00:37:44.640 --> 00:37:45.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>traditionnel.</c>

00:37:48.920 --> 00:37:51.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Cette route conduit</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à une zone touristique.</c>

00:37:57.320 --> 00:37:58.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Comme on va le voir, le tourisme</c>

00:37:59.320 --> 00:38:01.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>apporte de la nourriture</c>
<c.green.bg_black>aux communautés locales,</c>

00:38:02.160 --> 00:38:03.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>mais que des aliments</c>

00:38:03.880 --> 00:38:04.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés.</c>

00:38:10.440 --> 00:38:12.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Au cours</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des cinq dernières années,</c>

00:38:12.760 --> 00:38:14.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on a vu</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les habitants arrêtaient</c>

00:38:15.120 --> 00:38:16.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de plus en plus les voitures.</c>

00:38:16.840 --> 00:38:18.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils tendent une corde</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur la route</c>

00:38:18.800 --> 00:38:20.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour mendier de la nourriture.</c>

00:38:22.400 --> 00:38:25.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Conversations en espagnol</c>

