<c.green.bg_black>Des petits gâteaux.</c>

00:38:50.600 --> 00:38:51.920 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Des petits gâteaux ?</c>

00:38:52.880 --> 00:38:56.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai apporté des mandarines,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mais ils veulent des gâteaux.</c>

00:38:56.360 --> 00:38:59.120 line:79%
<c.green.bg_black>Tu en veux encore ?</c>
  <c.green.bg_black>-Oui, encore des petits gâteaux !</c>

00:39:04.520 --> 00:39:05.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Aujourd'hui, ils ont mangé</c>

00:39:06.240 --> 00:39:08.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des gâteaux et du chocolat.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Hier, ils ont mangé</c>

00:39:09.160 --> 00:39:10.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des biscuits.</c>

00:39:12.440 --> 00:39:14.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Le sucre, c'est addictif.</c>

00:39:15.880 --> 00:39:17.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ces enfants grandissent</c>

00:39:17.440 --> 00:39:19.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>en s'habituant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à manger des sucreries.</c>

00:39:20.400 --> 00:39:21.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils apprennent à aimer ça.</c>

00:39:23.480 --> 00:39:25.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est ce qu'on constate.</c>

00:39:25.600 --> 00:39:28.960 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ces aliments vont susciter</c>
<c.green.bg_black>un intérêt, chez eux.</c>

00:39:30.680 --> 00:39:32.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On voit</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les enfants sont attirés</c>

00:39:33.280 --> 00:39:35.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>par ces aliments riches en sucre,</c>

00:39:35.440 --> 00:39:37.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>en sel et en saveurs industrielles.</c>

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:41.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:39:41.440 --> 00:39:44.760 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:39:45.120 --> 00:39:49.000 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Je crois que ça y est, les aliments</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés se sont imposés</c>

00:39:49.360 --> 00:39:50.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>dans les cuisines, en Colombie.</c>

00:39:51.160 --> 00:39:52.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils représentent</c>

00:39:52.520 --> 00:39:55.440 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>une part importante</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des produits en supermarché.</c>

00:39:55.640 --> 00:39:58.120 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Propos en anglais</c>

00:39:58.480 --> 00:39:59.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>C'est une industrie puissante.</c>

00:40:00.120 --> 00:40:04.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Il y a de grandes entreprises</c>
<c.green.bg_black>derrière ce commerce d'aliments,</c>

00:40:04.480 --> 00:40:05.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et les Colombiens</c>

00:40:05.600 --> 00:40:07.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>en consomment beaucoup.</c>

00:40:10.880 --> 00:40:13.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle Juan Castro.</c>

00:40:13.360 --> 00:40:16.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis médecin et j'ai une maîtrise</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en santé publique.</c>

00:40:17.280 --> 00:40:18.560 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Dans les zones rurales,</c>

00:40:18.920 --> 00:40:22.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>beaucoup de gens</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ont peu de contact avec les villes.</c>

00:40:24.640 --> 00:40:26.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Le régime alimentaire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est différent.</c>

00:40:26.760 --> 00:40:29.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Là-bas, on mange encore</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du poisson et des fruits.</c>

00:40:31.960 --> 00:40:33.960 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Le vent souffle.</c>

00:40:34.160 --> 00:40:38.240 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>...</c>

00:40:38.600 --> 00:40:40.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Ça, c'est un plat traditionnel</c>

00:40:40.480 --> 00:40:42.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des Wayuu,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui vivent sur la côte.</c>

00:40:42.920 --> 00:40:44.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais la nouvelle génération</c>

00:40:44.680 --> 00:40:46.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ne veut plus manger ça.</c>

00:40:49.480 --> 00:40:51.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quand il n'y avait pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de sucre, les Wayuu</c>

00:40:52.200 --> 00:40:54.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>vivaient vieux</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et n'avaient pas de diabète.</c>

00:40:55.120 --> 00:40:56.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ce n'est plus le cas, aujourd'hui.</c>

00:40:57.080 --> 00:41:00.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les aliments transformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>provoquent ces maladies.</c>

00:41:00.480 --> 00:41:03.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On les mange, car ils sont</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pratiques et disponibles.</c>

00:41:06.880 --> 00:41:10.240 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Crépitement du feu</c>

00:41:10.600 --> 00:41:13.280 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Propos en espagnol</c>

00:41:13.480 --> 00:41:15.240 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Ces changements d'alimentation</c>

00:41:15.440 --> 00:41:17.760 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>n'entraînent pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que des maladies chroniques.</c>

00:41:18.120 --> 00:41:20.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils détruisent aussi</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la culture locale.</c>

00:41:23.480 --> 00:41:25.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>La cuisine traditionnelle disparaît.</c>

00:41:26.200 --> 00:41:29.560 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Les produits ultratransformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>deviennent des objets de désir.</c>

00:41:38.200 --> 00:41:39.920 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-La transformation des aliments</c>

00:41:40.280 --> 00:41:42.560 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>fait partie de l'évolution</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>des comportements.</c>

00:41:42.920 --> 00:41:44.680 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>On fait ça depuis des siècles,</c>

00:41:45.560 --> 00:41:47.480 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>que ce soit en cuisinant,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>en fumant,</c>

00:41:47.840 --> 00:41:49.040 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>en séchant, en salant</c>

00:41:49.400 --> 00:41:51.160 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ou en faisant mariner</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>la nourriture.</c>

00:41:53.360 --> 00:41:56.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais l'ultratransformation</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>est radicalement différente,</c>

00:41:56.800 --> 00:41:58.720 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>car elle utilise des additifs</c>

00:41:59.080 --> 00:42:00.080 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>non identifiables.</c>

00:42:01.680 --> 00:42:04.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Les additifs</c>
<c.green.bg_black>présents dans les aliments</c>

00:42:04.600 --> 00:42:07.440 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>peuvent avoir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une influence sur notre santé,</c>

00:42:07.640 --> 00:42:09.520 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>quelle que soit leur teneur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en éléments</c>

00:42:09.880 --> 00:42:10.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>nutritifs.</c>

00:42:10.920 --> 00:42:14.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quand on consomme beaucoup</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'aliments ultratransformés,</c>

00:42:14.240 --> 00:42:16.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on consomme beaucoup d'émulsifiants,</c>

00:42:16.840 --> 00:42:20.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>d'édulcorants artificiels,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de colorants, d'arômes.</c>

00:42:21.400 --> 00:42:25.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Autant de composés chimiques</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui ne sont pas des aliments.</c>

00:42:25.440 --> 00:42:28.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>En fait, notre corps</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ne sait pas métaboliser</c>

00:42:28.480 --> 00:42:29.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ces produits.</c>

00:42:34.240 --> 00:42:35.680 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Voyons ce qu'il y a,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>là-dedans.</c>

00:42:36.760 --> 00:42:38.120 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Inosinate disodique...</c>

00:42:38.480 --> 00:42:40.520 line:79% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Maltodextrine...</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-Perméat de lactosérum...</c>

00:42:40.880 --> 00:42:42.080 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Phosphate de potassium...</c>

00:42:42.440 --> 00:42:43.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Polydextrose...</c>

00:42:44.120 --> 00:42:45.200 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Glutamate monosodique...</c>

00:42:45.560 --> 00:42:47.480 line:79% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Acide citrique...</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-Chlorure de potassium...</c>

00:42:47.840 --> 00:42:49.720 line:79% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Émulsifiants...</c>
<c.green.bg_black>-Stabilisateurs...</c>

00:42:50.080 --> 00:42:51.600 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Ribonucléotide disodique...</c>

00:42:51.960 --> 00:42:55.600 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Hydroxypropylméthylcellulose,</c>

00:42:56.560 --> 00:42:59.360 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>gélifiants... Désolée,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>c'est pas de la nourriture.</c>

00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:05.000 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Ça ressemble à de la nourriture,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ça en a le goût,</c>

00:43:05.200 --> 00:43:08.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>mais de quoi sont faits</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>les aliments ultratransformés ?</c>

00:43:09.120 --> 00:43:11.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Pourquoi contiennent-ils</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>ces additifs ?</c>

00:43:13.840 --> 00:43:16.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-En tant que concepteur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de produits alimentaires...</c>

00:43:16.760 --> 00:43:18.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique douce</c>

00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:21.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On fait attention</c>
<c.green.bg_black>au coût des ingrédients,</c>

00:43:21.680 --> 00:43:23.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de la fabrication,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du transport.</c>

00:43:23.240 --> 00:43:25.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Du distributeur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>au détaillant, chacun</c>

00:43:25.360 --> 00:43:26.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>veut sa marge.</c>

00:43:27.720 --> 00:43:30.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Voici les ingrédients</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour faire</c>

00:43:30.440 --> 00:43:32.520 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>un gâteau au citron maison.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Il faut</c>

00:43:32.880 --> 00:43:36.320 line:83% align:center
