00:50:36.480 --> 00:50:39.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les ingrédients sur l'emballage,</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>même les additifs.</c>

00:50:39.560 --> 00:50:43.760 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:50:44.120 --> 00:50:45.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les gens ont commencé à lire</c>

00:50:46.280 --> 00:50:47.520 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>la composition des aliments.</c>

00:50:47.720 --> 00:50:50.360 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>En supermarché,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ils regardaient les étiquettes.</c>

00:50:51.320 --> 00:50:53.960 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>"Hydroxypropylméthylcellulose,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>c'est quoi ?"</c>

00:50:56.120 --> 00:50:57.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais comme les industriels</c>

00:50:57.840 --> 00:51:01.320 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>de l'agroalimentaire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ont toujours une longueur d'avance,</c>

00:51:01.680 --> 00:51:04.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ils ont proposé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'étiquetage propre.</c>

00:51:04.560 --> 00:51:06.560 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:51:06.760 --> 00:51:13.480 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:51:13.840 --> 00:51:17.080 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Ça consiste à rendre la composition</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des produits plus neutre</c>

00:51:17.440 --> 00:51:18.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour qu'elle présente mieux.</c>

00:51:19.240 --> 00:51:21.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:51:22.360 --> 00:51:23.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les additifs</c>

00:51:23.720 --> 00:51:25.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qui avaient mauvaise réputation</c>

00:51:25.440 --> 00:51:27.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ont été progressivement retirés.</c>

00:51:28.880 --> 00:51:31.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Des substituts</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sans doute aussi mauvais</c>

00:51:31.920 --> 00:51:33.240 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ont été introduits.</c>

00:51:34.240 --> 00:51:36.000 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Mais leur nom inquiète moins.</c>

00:51:36.200 --> 00:51:38.440 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Au lieu d'avoir la mention "arôme",</c>

00:51:38.640 --> 00:51:40.800 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>il y aura la mention</c>
<c.green.bg_black>"extrait de citron".</c>

00:51:44.760 --> 00:51:46.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais cet extrait de citron aura</c>

00:51:46.640 --> 00:51:48.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>été modifié par des procédés</c>

00:51:48.360 --> 00:51:49.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>chimiques ou mécaniques</c>

00:51:50.680 --> 00:51:54.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et il ne ressemblera pas du tout</c>
<c.green.bg_black>au jus de citron ou au zeste</c>

00:51:54.560 --> 00:51:56.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que j'utilise dans ma cuisine.</c>

00:51:59.720 --> 00:52:01.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:52:01.920 --> 00:52:05.080 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:52:05.440 --> 00:52:07.600 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Il y a aussi l'extrait de romarin.</c>

00:52:08.520 --> 00:52:10.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est une appellation poétique</c>

00:52:10.560 --> 00:52:12.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qui fait penser à un jardin en été.</c>

00:52:13.000 --> 00:52:14.560 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Chant d'oiseau</c>

00:52:15.880 --> 00:52:18.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Il s'agit en fait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'une formule très chimique</c>

00:52:18.720 --> 00:52:20.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>extraite du romarin.</c>

00:52:21.520 --> 00:52:24.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ça ne sent pas le romarin,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mais ça fait office</c>

00:52:24.440 --> 00:52:26.520 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>de conservateur alimentaire.</c>

00:52:28.160 --> 00:52:31.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Si vous voyez la mention</c>
<c.green.bg_black>"poudre d'épinards",</c>

00:52:31.280 --> 00:52:33.080 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>vous vous dites que c'est bon.</c>

00:52:33.440 --> 00:52:36.200 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Mais non,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>c'est sans doute un colorant vert.</c>

00:52:39.800 --> 00:52:41.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-J'ai participé à l'organisation</c>

00:52:42.320 --> 00:52:43.320 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>du lancement presse</c>

00:52:43.520 --> 00:52:45.600 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>d'un nouvel amidon</c>
<c.green.bg_black>modifié révolutionnaire.</c>

00:52:45.960 --> 00:52:47.520 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Propos en anglais</c>

00:52:47.720 --> 00:52:49.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Il constituait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une avancée considérable</c>

00:52:50.160 --> 00:52:51.480 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour les industriels.</c>

00:52:52.600 --> 00:52:55.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Il leur permettait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'apposer sur leurs emballages</c>

00:52:56.640 --> 00:52:58.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>la mention "artisanal", "naturel",</c>

00:52:59.880 --> 00:53:00.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"fait main".</c>

00:53:02.240 --> 00:53:03.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Cet amidon était</c>

00:53:03.720 --> 00:53:05.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>modifié de façon</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à permettre aux fabricants</c>

00:53:06.920 --> 00:53:08.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de mettre en valeur</c>
<c.green.bg_black>cet étiquetage</c>

00:53:08.920 --> 00:53:09.920 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>plus propre.</c>

00:53:11.160 --> 00:53:11.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Maintenant,</c>

00:53:13.240 --> 00:53:16.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ils peuvent dire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que ça s'apparente à du fait maison,</c>

00:53:16.480 --> 00:53:19.640 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>alors que ça n'a rien à voir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec ce qu'on fait chez soi.</c>

00:53:20.000 --> 00:53:22.720 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:53:23.080 --> 00:53:25.200 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Tout être vivant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est fait de substances</c>

00:53:25.560 --> 00:53:26.560 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>chimiques.</c>

00:53:26.760 --> 00:53:29.520 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Aujourd'hui, il y a une phobie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des produits chimiques</c>

00:53:29.720 --> 00:53:32.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>alimentée par certains</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui cherchent la petite bête.</c>

00:53:33.040 --> 00:53:35.640 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Vous consommeriez</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de l'hydroxyde d'hydrogène ?</c>

00:53:37.000 --> 00:53:37.800 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Non ?</c>

00:53:38.000 --> 00:53:40.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Vous allez mourir,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>car c'est de l'eau.</c>

00:53:43.120 --> 00:53:46.120 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Selon l'Autorité européenne</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de sécurité des aliments,</c>

00:53:46.320 --> 00:53:49.400 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ces additifs sont sans danger</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour la santé.</c>

00:53:49.600 --> 00:53:53.080 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais des scientifiques</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>s'interrogent sur le long terme.</c>

00:53:53.280 --> 00:53:55.000 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Bips de caisse</c>

00:53:55.360 --> 00:53:57.360 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:53:57.560 --> 00:54:00.920 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:54:01.280 --> 00:54:03.000 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>-Je suis</c>
<c.white.bg_black>le docteur Mathilde Touvier.</c>

00:54:03.200 --> 00:54:04.680 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>Je suis épidémiologiste.</c>

00:54:04.880 --> 00:54:08.200 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>Je dirige l'équipe de recherche</c>
<c.white.bg_black>en épidémiologie nutritionnelle</c>

00:54:08.400 --> 00:54:09.120 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>à l'INSERM.</c>

00:54:10.280 --> 00:54:12.880 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Nous avons lancé</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>l'étude NutriNet-Santé en 2009.</c>

00:54:13.080 --> 00:54:16.040 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Nous avons maintenant</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>plus de 14 ans de suivi.</c>

00:54:16.400 --> 00:54:20.680 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>Les participants,</c>
<c.white.bg_black>plus de 176 000 actuellement,</c>

00:54:20.880 --> 00:54:23.640 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>remplissent des questionnaires</c>
<c.white.bg_black>sur leur alimentation.</c>

00:54:24.000 --> 00:54:26.000 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>Certains vont développer</c>
<c.white.bg_black>des pathologies.</c>

00:54:26.200 --> 00:54:30.880 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>Ça nous permet d'étudier les liens</c>
<c.white.bg_black>entre ces expositions aux additifs</c>

00:54:31.080 --> 00:54:33.360 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>et le risque</c>
<c.white.bg_black>de développer un cancer,</c>

00:54:33.560 --> 00:54:34.840 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>une maladie cardiovasculaire,</c>

00:54:35.040 --> 00:54:37.120 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>de l'obésité</c>
<c.white.bg_black>ou un diabète de type 2.</c>

00:54:37.480 --> 00:54:40.440 line:83% align:right
<c.white.bg_black>Ici, on a les échantillons</c>
<c.white.bg_black>de l'étude NutriNet-Santé,</c>

00:54:40.640 --> 00:54:44.920 line:83% align:right
<c.white.bg_black>des échantillons</c>
<c.white.bg_black>d'urine et de plasma,</c>

00:54:45.120 --> 00:54:48.000 line:83% align:right
<c.white.bg_black>qui nous permettent</c>
<c.white.bg_black>d'évaluer certains biomarqueurs.</c>

00:54:49.960 --> 00:54:53.120 line:83% align:right
<c.white.bg_black>On peut apporter des arguments</c>
<c.white.bg_black>en faveur de la causalité</c>

00:54:53.480 --> 00:54:56.960 line:83% align:right
<c.white.bg_black>des associations additifs,</c>
<c.white.bg_black>aliments ultratransformés</c>

00:54:57.160 --> 00:54:58.240 line:91% align:right
<c.white.bg_black>et risques de maladies.</c>

00:54:59.280 --> 00:55:01.040 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Heureusement, sur le marché,</c>

00:55:01.240 --> 00:55:04.520 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>la plupart des additifs</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>sont probablement sans danger.</c>

00:55:04.720 --> 00:55:06.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:55:07.040 --> 00:55:09.320 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Cela est à prendre en considération.</c>

00:55:09.520 --> 00:55:11.080 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Ils ont été autorisés</c>

00:55:11.440 --> 00:55:15.720 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>et évalués par l'EFSA, l'Autorité</c>
<c.white.bg_black>européenne de sécurité des aliments.</c>

00:55:16.800 --> 00:55:18.120 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Mais c'était sur la base</c>

00:55:18.320 --> 00:55:20.360 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>de la littérature</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>scientifique disponible</c>

00:55:20.560 --> 00:55:22.120 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>à un certain moment.</c>

00:55:22.920 --> 00:55:24.800 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>On doit vraiment réévaluer</c>

00:55:25.000 --> 00:55:27.320 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>les dangers potentiels</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>de certains additifs</c>

00:55:27.520 --> 00:55:30.240 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>à la lumière</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>des nouvelles preuves disponibles.</c>

00:55:31.600 --> 00:55:34.480 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>Par définition, les aliments</c>
<c.white.bg_black>ultratransformés contiennent</c>

00:55:34.840 --> 00:55:36.680 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>des additifs alimentaires.</c>

00:55:36.880 --> 00:55:40.400 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>En Europe, on en compte 330</c>
<c.white.bg_black>qui sont autorisés.</c>

00:55:40.760 --> 00:55:43.880 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Dans l'étude NutriNet-Santé,</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>nous avons compté</c>

00:55:44.240 --> 00:55:47.520 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>que nous ingérions environ 4 kg</c>

00:55:47.880 --> 00:55:49.480 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>d'additifs alimentaires par an.</c>

00:55:50.760 --> 00:55:54.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les émulsifiants sont un groupe</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'additifs couramment utilisés,</c>

00:55:54.880 --> 00:55:56.520 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>notamment</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>dans le pain industriel,</c>

00:55:56.720 --> 00:55:59.840 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les sauces préparées</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>et presque tous les assaisonnements.</c>

00:56:01.480 --> 00:56:03.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les émulsifiants</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sont très utilisés</c>

00:56:03.840 --> 00:56:06.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>dans l'industrie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour lier les ingrédients.</c>

00:56:09.880 --> 00:56:12.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quand on met un corps gras</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec quelque chose</c>

00:56:12.600 --> 00:56:15.800 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>à base d'eau, comme du vinaigre,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on a beau les mélanger,</c>

00:56:16.160 --> 00:56:17.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ils vont se séparer.</c>

00:56:20.040 --> 00:56:23.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>L'utilisation d'un émulsifiant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>permet de les faire tenir</c>

00:56:24.000 --> 00:56:26.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ensemble pour que le mélange</c>
<c.green.bg_black>reste homogène.</c>

00:56:30.080 --> 00:56:33.000 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Les chercheurs se demandent</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>si des émulsifiants</c>

00:56:33.200 --> 00:56:35.040 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>n'agiraient pas</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>comme des détergents</c>

00:56:35.240 --> 00:56:38.160 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>en éliminant le mucus protecteur</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de l'intestin.</c>

00:56:38.520 --> 00:56:40.840 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Cela pourrait</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>perturber le microbiote,</c>

00:56:41.040 --> 00:56:44.360 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>l'ensemble des microorganismes</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>qui participent à la digestion,</c>

00:56:44.560 --> 00:56:46.880 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>avec des conséquences</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>potentiellement graves.</c>

00:56:48.520 --> 00:56:50.160 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>-Concernant les émulsifiants,</c>

00:56:50.360 --> 00:56:53.920 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>on a de plus en plus d'éléments</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>provenant d'études expérimentales</c>

00:56:54.120 --> 00:56:57.040 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>montrant qu'ils impactent</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>le microbiote intestinal,</c>

00:56:57.400 --> 00:56:59.800 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>qu'ils augmentent</c>
<c.white.bg_black>l'inflammation chronique</c>

00:57:00.000 --> 00:57:03.080 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>et qu'ils favoriseraient,</c>
<c.white.bg_black>sur des modèles animaux,</c>

00:57:03.280 --> 00:57:04.760 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>la carcinogenèse</c>

00:57:05.120 --> 00:57:06.320 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>au niveau colorectal.</c>

00:57:10.320 --> 00:57:13.880 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>On n'est pas encore sûrs</c>
<c.white.bg_black>à 100 % de l'impact délétère</c>

00:57:14.240 --> 00:57:15.880 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>des émulsifiants sur la santé,</c>

00:57:16.080 --> 00:57:17.720 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>mais on a</c>
<c.white.bg_black>des preuves scientifiques</c>

00:57:18.080 --> 00:57:19.920 line:91% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>qui s'accumulent de plus en plus</c>

00:57:20.280 --> 00:57:23.960 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>pour suggérer qu'ils pourraient</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>causer des problèmes de santé.</c>

00:57:25.320 --> 00:57:28.240 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>Quand ces additifs ont été autorisés</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>pour la 1re fois,</c>

00:57:28.440 --> 00:57:29.640 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>on n'avait pas ces études</c>

00:57:30.000 --> 00:57:33.160 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>sur le microbiote intestinal,</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>l'impact sur le métabolisme</c>

00:57:33.360 --> 00:57:34.680 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>ou ces études de cohorte</c>

00:57:35.040 --> 00:57:38.280 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>qui apportent des informations</c>
<c.white.bg_black>sur la santé à long terme.</c>

00:57:38.480 --> 00:57:41.200 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>Donc,</c>
<c.white.bg_black>toutes ces nouvelles informations</c>

00:57:41.560 --> 00:57:44.800 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>doivent être prises en compte</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>pour réévaluer ces additifs.</c>

00:57:45.000 --> 00:57:47.360 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

00:57:47.560 --> 00:57:49.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les aliments ultratransformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>présentent</c>

00:57:49.920 --> 00:57:51.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de nombreux avantages.</c>

00:57:51.320 --> 00:57:55.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils sont bon marché, pratiques,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>savoureux, ne nécessitent pas</c>

00:57:55.520 --> 00:57:58.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>beaucoup d'équipements</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ni de compétences de préparation.</c>

00:57:58.760 --> 00:58:00.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils se conservent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>longtemps en rayon</c>

00:58:01.040 --> 00:58:02.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et ils ne s'abîment pas.</c>

00:58:04.040 --> 00:58:07.280 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>La question est de savoir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>si ces aliments sont dangereux.</c>

00:58:07.480 --> 00:58:10.120 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Aujourd'hui,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on n'a pas encore la réponse.</c>

00:58:12.440 --> 00:58:14.440 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Exploiter le système de récompense</c>

00:58:14.800 --> 00:58:15.800 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>du cerveau,</c>

