<c.cyan.bg_black>garantir le point de félicité</c>

00:58:18.280 --> 00:58:21.960 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et utiliser des techniques</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>de marketing hyper sophistiquées</c>

00:58:22.160 --> 00:58:23.920 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>provoque</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>un phénomène inquiétant</c>

00:58:24.120 --> 00:58:26.480 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sur lequel des études</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>commencent à se pencher :</c>

00:58:26.680 --> 00:58:27.880 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>l'addiction.</c>

00:58:28.240 --> 00:58:30.240 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique dynamique</c>

00:58:30.440 --> 00:58:36.160 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:58:36.360 --> 00:58:38.360 line:79% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>
<c.red.bg_black>Applaudissements</c>

00:58:38.720 --> 00:58:40.760 line:79% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>
<c.red.bg_black>...</c>

00:58:42.120 --> 00:58:43.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Je suis ravie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'être ici aujourd'hui</c>

00:58:44.160 --> 00:58:45.840 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour vous parler de mes recherches</c>

00:58:46.040 --> 00:58:49.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>sur les similitudes entre substances</c>
<c.green.bg_black>addictives et aliments</c>

00:58:49.760 --> 00:58:50.800 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés.</c>

00:58:52.960 --> 00:58:54.880 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis Ashley Gearhardt,</c>

00:58:55.080 --> 00:58:58.160 line:54% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>professeure de psychologie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à l'université du Michigan</c>

00:58:58.360 --> 00:59:01.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et directrice du Food and Addiction</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Science and Treatment Lab.</c>

00:59:02.440 --> 00:59:03.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le gras</c>

00:59:03.760 --> 00:59:05.560 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et le sucre activent le circuit</c>

00:59:05.920 --> 00:59:07.480 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>neuronal de la récompense.</c>

00:59:07.680 --> 00:59:09.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Il semble</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les produits hyperappétissants</c>

00:59:10.240 --> 00:59:11.280 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ont un profil identique</c>

00:59:11.640 --> 00:59:13.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>à celui des drogues addictives.</c>

00:59:14.760 --> 00:59:16.120 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Quand on regarde les aliments</c>

00:59:16.320 --> 00:59:18.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qui déclenchent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les marqueurs de dépendance,</c>

00:59:18.880 --> 00:59:22.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>on voit que ce ne sont pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les aliments peu transformés</c>

00:59:22.240 --> 00:59:23.800 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>comme les fruits, les légumes,</c>

00:59:24.160 --> 00:59:27.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>les haricots</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ou les viandes maigres</c>

00:59:27.360 --> 00:59:28.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>comme le blanc de poulet.</c>

00:59:29.840 --> 00:59:32.200 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ce sont les aliments</c>
<c.green.bg_black>transformés contenant</c>

00:59:32.560 --> 00:59:34.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de forts taux de glucides raffinés,</c>

00:59:34.840 --> 00:59:37.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des sucres et des amidons,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>généralement associés</c>

00:59:37.920 --> 00:59:40.760 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>à une grande quantité</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de matières grasses.</c>

00:59:41.120 --> 00:59:43.480 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

00:59:43.840 --> 00:59:49.280 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

00:59:49.480 --> 00:59:51.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le pouvoir de récompense</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de ces aliments</c>

00:59:51.760 --> 00:59:53.600 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés est tel</c>

00:59:54.000 --> 00:59:55.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il peut déclencher</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une dépendance</c>

00:59:56.160 --> 00:59:59.440 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qui pousse les personnes</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à une consommation compulsive.</c>

00:59:59.640 --> 01:00:00.880 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Même si elles savent</c>

01:00:01.240 --> 01:00:04.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qu'elles peuvent en mourir,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>elles ne peuvent pas s'arrêter.</c>

01:00:04.640 --> 01:00:06.640 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

01:00:06.840 --> 01:00:10.160 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:00:10.360 --> 01:00:13.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les aliments transformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>contrôlent ma vie.</c>

01:00:13.240 --> 01:00:15.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je ne veux pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>me gaver de brocolis.</c>

01:00:15.560 --> 01:00:17.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je veux manger</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ces produits de merde.</c>

01:00:20.560 --> 01:00:23.200 line:58% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle Sarita,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>j'ai 48 ans</c>

01:00:23.560 --> 01:00:25.200 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et je suis accro à la nourriture.</c>

01:00:27.520 --> 01:00:29.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Manger en voiture</c>

01:00:29.240 --> 01:00:32.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>est un phénomène répandu</c>
<c.green.bg_black>chez les personnes comme moi.</c>

01:00:32.800 --> 01:00:35.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>En rentrant chez soi,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on va dans un magasin,</c>

01:00:35.560 --> 01:00:39.200 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>on achète des barres chocolatées</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et on les mange au volant.</c>

01:00:41.400 --> 01:00:42.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>À la maison,</c>

01:00:42.760 --> 01:00:45.680 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>je continue</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec des céréales très sucrées.</c>

01:00:46.040 --> 01:00:48.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'en verse un maximum</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans un saladier.</c>

01:00:48.800 --> 01:00:51.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Pas dans un bol, dans un saladier.</c>

01:00:51.400 --> 01:00:53.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Et je commence par ça.</c>

01:00:54.760 --> 01:00:56.560 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Je mange tout le paquet,</c>

01:00:57.080 --> 01:00:59.320 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>plus 3 ou 4 barres chocolatées,</c>

01:00:59.520 --> 01:01:01.640 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et 2 ou 3 paquets de biscuits.</c>

01:01:01.840 --> 01:01:02.800 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>On n'imagine pas</c>

01:01:03.000 --> 01:01:05.680 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>que quelqu'un mange autant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en si peu de temps.</c>

01:01:08.120 --> 01:01:09.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ensuite, j'essaie</c>

01:01:09.480 --> 01:01:11.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>d'expulser ça au plus vite.</c>

01:01:12.600 --> 01:01:14.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"Expulser",</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ça veut dire se faire vomir.</c>

01:01:17.120 --> 01:01:20.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis intelligente,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>je fais beaucoup de sport.</c>

01:01:21.640 --> 01:01:24.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Je sais que cette boulimie</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est très mauvaise pour moi.</c>

01:01:24.840 --> 01:01:26.960 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

01:01:27.160 --> 01:01:29.240 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Elle peut entraîner</c>
<c.green.bg_black>une crise cardiaque,</c>

01:01:29.440 --> 01:01:31.240 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>du diabète, et j'en passe.</c>

01:01:32.120 --> 01:01:34.400 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Mais ce qui montre</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que c'est une addiction,</c>

01:01:34.600 --> 01:01:37.120 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>c'est que ça ne change rien.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'en fiche.</c>

01:01:38.680 --> 01:01:42.600 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Que ça puisse me faire du mal,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>voire me tuer, ça ne m'arrête pas.</c>

01:01:45.960 --> 01:01:47.760 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Drogue et alcool sont plus faciles</c>

01:01:48.120 --> 01:01:50.320 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>à abandonner que la nourriture,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on est</c>

01:01:50.680 --> 01:01:52.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>obligés de manger pour vivre.</c>

01:01:55.400 --> 01:01:58.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Mais comment arrêter de consommer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ces aliments transformés ?</c>

01:01:58.920 --> 01:02:00.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils sont partout.</c>

01:02:05.400 --> 01:02:07.320 line:58% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Des industriels ont fait passer</c>

01:02:07.680 --> 01:02:08.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des scanners</c>

01:02:08.880 --> 01:02:10.480 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>à des gens pour observer</c>

01:02:10.840 --> 01:02:12.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ce qui se passait dans leur tête</c>

01:02:12.760 --> 01:02:14.760 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>quand ils testaient leurs produits.</c>

01:02:14.960 --> 01:02:16.760 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

01:02:17.680 --> 01:02:20.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je ne sais pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>s'ils avaient l'intention de rendre</c>

01:02:20.600 --> 01:02:24.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ces aliments addictifs...</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Mais ce qu'on peut dire,</c>

01:02:24.520 --> 01:02:28.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>c'est que si vous consommez</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les produits d'une marque</c>

01:02:28.360 --> 01:02:31.080 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ayant appartenu</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à un fabricant de tabac,</c>

01:02:31.880 --> 01:02:34.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>il y a des chances</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'ils aient été conçus</c>

01:02:34.240 --> 01:02:35.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour que vous vouliez</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en manger plus.</c>

01:02:36.320 --> 01:02:37.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Propos en anglais</c>

01:02:40.680 --> 01:02:43.680 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Un point de vue réfuté</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>par les professionnels.</c>

01:02:45.640 --> 01:02:47.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Il faut</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que les produits soient bons.</c>

01:02:48.040 --> 01:02:51.600 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Mais le bon</c>
<c.green.bg_black>s'est transformé en trop bon,</c>

01:02:51.800 --> 01:02:54.040 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>en addictif, en trop savoureux.</c>

01:02:54.400 --> 01:02:56.000 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Est-ce qu'on peut faire en sorte</c>

01:02:56.200 --> 01:02:58.120 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>qu'un produit</c>
<c.green.bg_black>soit suffisamment bon</c>

01:02:58.320 --> 01:02:59.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour qu'on veuille le manger,</c>

01:02:59.960 --> 01:03:03.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>mais pas trop pour qu'il ne soit pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>hyperappétissant ?</c>

01:03:04.200 --> 01:03:05.520 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Oui, mais dès qu'il y aura</c>

01:03:05.880 --> 01:03:09.560 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>un produit hyperappétissant,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on arrêtera de manger les autres.</c>

01:03:11.920 --> 01:03:14.600 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On n'imposera pas aux industriels</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de fabriquer</c>

01:03:14.800 --> 01:03:17.720 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>de mauvais produits,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le monde deviendrait triste.</c>

01:03:20.120 --> 01:03:23.120 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Au vu des similitudes de stratégie</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>entre l'industrie</c>

01:03:23.480 --> 01:03:25.680 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>agroalimentaire et celle du tabac,</c>

01:03:26.040 --> 01:03:28.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>comment réagiront-elles</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>aux allégations</c>

01:03:28.560 --> 01:03:30.760 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'accoutumances</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>aux aliments ultratransformés</c>

01:03:30.960 --> 01:03:32.240 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sachant que pendant des années,</c>

01:03:32.600 --> 01:03:36.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>les fabricants de tabac ont nié</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>l'aspect addictif des produits ?</c>

01:03:38.040 --> 01:03:40.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique douce</c>

01:03:40.240 --> 01:03:43.360 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:03:43.720 --> 01:03:46.600 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-Je m'appelle Steve Parrish,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>retraité depuis 2008.</c>

01:03:46.800 --> 01:03:48.160 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai quitté Altria Inc.,</c>

01:03:48.520 --> 01:03:51.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>anciennement connu</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sous le nom de Philip Morris.</c>

01:03:53.240 --> 01:03:55.880 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'y exerçais</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la fonction de vice-président.</c>

01:03:57.440 --> 01:03:59.760 line:66% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>La cigarette ne modifie ni l'humeur</c>

01:03:59.960 --> 01:04:02.960 line:58% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ni la capacité à avoir</c>
<c.green.bg_black>un comportement normal.</c>

01:04:03.640 --> 01:04:06.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ceux qui qualifient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le tabagisme de dépendance</c>

01:04:06.440 --> 01:04:09.080 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le font pour des raisons politiques</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et idéologiques,</c>

01:04:09.280 --> 01:04:10.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pas scientifiques.</c>

01:04:11.560 --> 01:04:14.240 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Aux États-Unis,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>au début des années 90,</c>

01:04:14.440 --> 01:04:15.440 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>l'attitude à l'égard</c>

01:04:15.800 --> 01:04:17.480 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de l'industrie du tabac</c>

01:04:17.840 --> 01:04:19.520 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>a radicalement changé.</c>

01:04:19.880 --> 01:04:21.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>L'année 1994</c>

01:04:21.400 --> 01:04:23.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>a été le point culminant</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de la tempête,</c>

01:04:23.640 --> 01:04:26.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>avec une commission</c>
<c.green.bg_black>d'enquête au Congrès.</c>

01:04:27.000 --> 01:04:29.480 line:66% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Vous êtes maintenant sous serment.</c>

01:04:30.000 --> 01:04:31.280 line:70% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-La commission a demandé</c>

01:04:31.640 --> 01:04:33.160 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>aux PDG de l'industrie du tabac :</c>

01:04:33.360 --> 01:04:36.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>"Pensez-vous que la cigarette</c>
<c.green.bg_black>crée une dépendance ?"</c>

01:04:36.400 --> 01:04:38.000 line:66% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-La nicotine n'est pas addictive ?</c>

01:04:38.360 --> 01:04:39.960 line:66% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Elle n'est pas addictive.</c>

01:04:40.320 --> 01:04:43.360 line:58% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>-La cigarette et la nicotine</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ne correspondent pas</c>

01:04:43.560 --> 01:04:45.080 line:70% align:center
