01:11:35.520 --> 01:11:39.040 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>aucun secteur n'a jamais réussi</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à s'autoréguler.</c>

01:11:39.720 --> 01:11:42.640 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Ni le pétrole,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ni l'automobile, ni l'aviation,</c>

01:11:42.840 --> 01:11:44.360 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ni l'industrie pharmaceutique.</c>

01:11:44.560 --> 01:11:45.920 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Ça ne s'est jamais vu.</c>

01:11:48.720 --> 01:11:51.120 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique mystérieuse</c>

01:11:51.320 --> 01:11:53.560 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:11:53.920 --> 01:11:55.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Comme l'agroalimentaire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>veut moins</c>

01:11:56.000 --> 01:11:57.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de réglementation sur ses produits,</c>

01:11:58.040 --> 01:12:01.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le lobbying est très agressif</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans tous les pays.</c>

01:12:01.480 --> 01:12:04.920 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:12:05.280 --> 01:12:06.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis Mélissa Mialon.</c>

01:12:07.560 --> 01:12:09.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'étais ingénieure agroalimentaire,</c>

01:12:09.880 --> 01:12:12.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>mais je n'étais pas d'accord</c>
<c.green.bg_black>avec les pratiques</c>

01:12:12.720 --> 01:12:14.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ni avec les ingrédients utilisés.</c>

01:12:17.720 --> 01:12:20.480 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Aujourd'hui, je veux révéler</c>
<c.green.bg_black>comment elle procède</c>

01:12:20.840 --> 01:12:21.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et pourquoi.</c>

01:12:26.360 --> 01:12:27.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ce que nos recherches</c>

01:12:27.760 --> 01:12:29.440 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>ont montré,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>c'est que les industriels</c>

01:12:29.800 --> 01:12:31.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>se battent contre l'idée</c>

01:12:31.960 --> 01:12:34.920 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>que l'ultratransformation</c>
<c.green.bg_black>nuit à la santé.</c>

01:12:35.280 --> 01:12:37.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils essaient aussi</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de développer leurs propres</c>

01:12:38.160 --> 01:12:40.520 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>études scientifiques</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et de créer un réseau</c>

01:12:40.880 --> 01:12:42.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de publications parallèles.</c>

01:12:43.600 --> 01:12:44.640 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-"Ces enquêtes</c>

01:12:45.000 --> 01:12:48.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ne montrent aucun lien</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>entre l'indice de masse corporelle</c>

01:12:48.400 --> 01:12:50.960 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>et la consommation</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'aliments ultratransformés."</c>

01:12:51.840 --> 01:12:53.360 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-L'étude de Mélissa Mialon</c>

01:12:53.560 --> 01:12:55.560 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>a révélé</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>que sur 38 articles portant</c>

01:12:55.920 --> 01:12:57.560 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>sur les aliments ultratransformés,</c>

01:12:57.760 --> 01:13:00.200 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>33 ont des auteurs</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>liés à l'agroalimentaire.</c>

01:13:00.400 --> 01:13:02.000 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

01:13:02.200 --> 01:13:04.000 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:13:04.360 --> 01:13:05.840 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Il devient difficile de savoir</c>

01:13:06.200 --> 01:13:08.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ce qui est scientifiquement vrai,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>car ces études</c>

01:13:09.240 --> 01:13:11.720 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>sont financées par les industriels.</c>

01:13:12.080 --> 01:13:14.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>C'est la fabrique du doute.</c>

01:13:14.240 --> 01:13:16.440 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:13:18.000 --> 01:13:21.120 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>-Ces entreprises veulent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>entrer en contact avec moi,</c>

01:13:21.320 --> 01:13:23.320 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>m'inviter</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à donner des conférences,</c>

01:13:23.520 --> 01:13:26.000 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>à faire des exposés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>outre-Atlantique.</c>

01:13:26.360 --> 01:13:28.840 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:13:29.040 --> 01:13:31.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>En règle générale, je refuse.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Mais une fois,</c>

01:13:31.920 --> 01:13:33.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>je me suis dit :</c>

01:13:33.200 --> 01:13:35.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"Voyons</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à quoi ressemble ce contrat."</c>

01:13:38.000 --> 01:13:39.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-C'était une entreprise connue ?</c>

01:13:39.840 --> 01:13:42.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Oui, un grand groupe</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de l'agroalimentaire.</c>

01:13:43.720 --> 01:13:45.640 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai reçu le contrat.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Ils me proposaient</c>

01:13:46.000 --> 01:13:49.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>près de 20 000 livres sterling</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour une réunion de 2 heures.</c>

01:13:50.080 --> 01:13:52.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je ne comprenais pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pourquoi ils me payaient autant.</c>

01:13:53.160 --> 01:13:54.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai montré</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ce contrat à un avocat.</c>

01:13:55.000 --> 01:13:57.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Voici la partie intéressante.</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Elle stipule</c>

01:13:58.040 --> 01:13:59.960 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que je ne ferai aucune déclaration</c>

01:14:00.160 --> 01:14:03.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>susceptible de dénigrer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'entreprise, ses produits</c>

01:14:04.400 --> 01:14:06.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ou de jeter</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le discrédit sur son nom.</c>

01:14:07.840 --> 01:14:09.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, pour 20 000 livres,</c>

01:14:09.800 --> 01:14:12.880 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ils voulaient acheter mon silence</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur leurs produits.</c>

01:14:13.240 --> 01:14:15.800 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique sombre</c>

01:14:16.000 --> 01:14:16.800 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>-Il a fallu</c>

01:14:17.160 --> 01:14:20.800 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>des années pour que l'industrie</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>du tabac soit contrôlée.</c>

01:14:21.000 --> 01:14:22.520 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>Mais dès à présent,</c>

01:14:22.880 --> 01:14:25.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>des gouvernements</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>d'Amériques centrale et du Sud</c>

01:14:25.800 --> 01:14:27.280 line:91% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>ont voulu créer des politiques</c>

01:14:27.640 --> 01:14:29.440 line:83% align:center
<c.cyan.bg_black>alimentaires</c>
<c.cyan.bg_black>pour changer la donne.</c>

01:14:31.720 --> 01:14:33.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les maladies chroniques</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mobilisent 70</c>

01:14:34.280 --> 01:14:36.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>à 80 % des ressources</c>
<c.green.bg_black>consacrées à la santé.</c>

01:14:37.960 --> 01:14:41.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le poids des gens a doublé,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ces dernières décennies.</c>

01:14:42.320 --> 01:14:44.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le diabète, le cancer, l'obésité</c>

01:14:44.880 --> 01:14:47.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>sont liés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>aux aliments ultratransformés.</c>

01:14:49.160 --> 01:14:51.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On ne peut pas se cacher</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la tête dans le sable</c>

01:14:51.720 --> 01:14:54.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et se dire que les choses</c>
<c.green.bg_black>changeront d'elles-mêmes.</c>

01:14:55.960 --> 01:14:58.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis médecin,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et je suis devenu sénateur,</c>

01:14:58.880 --> 01:15:02.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>car je voulais faire évoluer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le système de santé colombien.</c>

01:15:02.720 --> 01:15:05.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Il fallait avant tout</c>
<c.green.bg_black>travailler sur la prévention</c>

01:15:05.920 --> 01:15:07.400 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et faire passer une loi.</c>

01:15:09.640 --> 01:15:11.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On a d'abord proposé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de mettre en place</c>

01:15:12.160 --> 01:15:14.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des étiquettes d'avertissement,</c>

01:15:14.200 --> 01:15:16.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>puis une taxe sur les aliments</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés</c>

01:15:17.160 --> 01:15:21.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pour que le système de santé ait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>plus d'argent pour soigner.</c>

01:15:25.960 --> 01:15:28.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Pour moi, il était clair</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'il fallait agir.</c>

01:15:31.080 --> 01:15:32.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les entreprises agroalimentaires</c>

01:15:33.040 --> 01:15:35.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ont eu du mal à s'opposer à ça.</c>

01:15:36.800 --> 01:15:38.080 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, leurs représentants</c>

01:15:38.440 --> 01:15:41.920 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>m'ont invité dans des lieux</c>
<c.green.bg_black>touristiques de Colombie.</c>

01:15:42.280 --> 01:15:45.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ils voulaient me parler</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour me dissuader d'agir.</c>

01:15:47.440 --> 01:15:50.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Je n'ai jamais accepté,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>parce que j'avais été mis en garde.</c>

01:15:51.600 --> 01:15:56.000 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je ne suis pas conspirationniste,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mais ce genre de pratiques existent.</c>

01:16:01.560 --> 01:16:05.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai exposé les faits aux électeurs</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur les réseaux sociaux</c>

01:16:05.320 --> 01:16:06.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et j'ai présenté</c>

01:16:06.720 --> 01:16:08.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ce projet de loi,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui a suscité</c>

01:16:08.640 --> 01:16:10.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>une certaine résistance.</c>

01:16:10.840 --> 01:16:13.560 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Certains élus</c>
<c.green.bg_black>n'ont pas voulu le soutenir.</c>

01:16:14.440 --> 01:16:17.680 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Mais en sensibilisant les gens,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>le combat était plus facile.</c>

01:16:21.360 --> 01:16:23.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les sénateurs aussi ont des enfants.</c>

01:16:24.240 --> 01:16:26.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Parleront-ils au Congrès</c>
<c.green.bg_black>devant tout le monde</c>

01:16:27.320 --> 01:16:30.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour défendre quelque chose</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de mauvais pour leur santé ?</c>

01:16:32.320 --> 01:16:35.440 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Ça a pris trois ans</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et nécessité quelques compromis,</c>

01:16:35.800 --> 01:16:38.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>mais quand le projet de loi final</c>
<c.green.bg_black>a été présenté,</c>

01:16:38.800 --> 01:16:39.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>ils m'ont soutenu</c>

01:16:40.160 --> 01:16:41.280 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et ont voté pour.</c>

01:16:49.040 --> 01:16:51.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les étiquettes d'avertissement</c>
<c.green.bg_black>indiquent la quantité</c>

01:16:52.040 --> 01:16:54.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de sucres, de calories,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de gras et de sel.</c>

01:16:57.840 --> 01:17:01.960 line:91% align:center
<c.red.bg_black>Vrombissements robotiques</c>

01:17:05.200 --> 01:17:07.040 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>C'était vraiment gratifiant.</c>

01:17:07.560 --> 01:17:08.560 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis fier</c>

01:17:08.920 --> 01:17:10.800 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>d'avoir participé à ce combat</c>

01:17:11.160 --> 01:17:13.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour que les gens mangent mieux.</c>

01:17:15.720 --> 01:17:19.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Comme les entreprises ne sont pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>capables de s'autoréguler,</c>

01:17:19.200 --> 01:17:21.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>les gouvernements</c>
<c.green.bg_black>doivent intervenir.</c>

01:17:21.720 --> 01:17:23.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Si l'essence est sans plomb,</c>

01:17:23.520 --> 01:17:26.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>si je ne suis pas là avec vous</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en train de fumer,</c>

01:17:27.040 --> 01:17:30.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>si les voitures sont équipées</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de ceintures de sécurité,</c>

01:17:30.440 --> 01:17:32.840 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>c'est parce que</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les gouvernements l'ont exigé,</c>

01:17:33.040 --> 01:17:34.600 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et on s'en porte tous mieux.</c>

01:17:35.400 --> 01:17:37.680 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Maintenant, ils doivent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mettre en place</c>

01:17:37.880 --> 01:17:39.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>une vraie réglementation</c>

01:17:39.560 --> 01:17:43.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>qui encourage une alimentation saine</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et décourage la malbouffe.</c>

01:17:49.720 --> 01:17:52.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Les industriels ont dépensé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des milliards de dollars</c>

01:17:52.600 --> 01:17:54.120 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>pour trouver le goût et l'aspect</c>

01:17:54.480 --> 01:17:56.040 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>parfaits pour leurs produits</c>

01:17:56.400 --> 01:17:58.000 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et créer des stratégies marketing.</c>

01:18:01.760 --> 01:18:03.200 line:62% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Pourquoi ne pas se dire :</c>

01:18:03.400 --> 01:18:05.680 line:58% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>"Comment rendre mes produits</c>
<c.green.bg_black>plus sains ?</c>

01:18:06.040 --> 01:18:07.720 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Comment leur donner bon goût</c>

01:18:08.080 --> 01:18:09.440 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>avec moins de sucre ?"</c>

01:18:12.320 --> 01:18:13.480 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Je suis Greg Garrett.</c>

01:18:13.680 --> 01:18:16.360 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Je dirige la fondation</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Access to Nutrition Initiative.</c>

01:18:18.400 --> 01:18:22.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Notre objectif est d'améliorer</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'accès aux aliments sains.</c>

01:18:22.760 --> 01:18:25.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On travaille avec</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les investisseurs et actionnaires</c>

01:18:25.960 --> 01:18:27.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des géants de l'agroalimentaire,</c>

01:18:28.080 --> 01:18:29.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>dont les noms nous sont familiers.</c>

01:18:30.600 --> 01:18:33.240 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Nestlé, Danone, Frieslandcampina,</c>

01:18:33.440 --> 01:18:37.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Unilever, Kellogg's,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>Coca-Cola, Pepsi.</c>

01:18:39.120 --> 01:18:42.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On fait directement pression</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur les conseils d'administration</c>

01:18:42.720 --> 01:18:46.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et les PDG pour qu'ils initient</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de vrais changements,</c>

01:18:46.960 --> 01:18:50.920 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>que d'ici cinq ans, ils s'axent plus</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur la prévention de l'obésité</c>

01:18:51.280 --> 01:18:53.240 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>et des carences</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en micronutriments</c>

01:18:53.440 --> 01:18:55.600 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>afin de régler</c>
<c.green.bg_black>les problèmes actuels</c>

01:18:55.960 --> 01:18:57.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>imputables à cette industrie.</c>

01:18:59.320 --> 01:19:01.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On demande aux entreprises</c>

01:19:01.640 --> 01:19:04.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>d'agir dès maintenant,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de revoir leurs produits,</c>

01:19:04.640 --> 01:19:07.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de renoncer à certains</c>

01:19:07.640 --> 01:19:10.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et d'en proposer de nouveaux</c>
<c.green.bg_black>plus équilibrés,</c>

01:19:10.640 --> 01:19:13.400 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de façon à ce que 50 %</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de leur catalogue</c>

01:19:13.760 --> 01:19:15.200 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>soit composé de produits sains.</c>

01:19:17.440 --> 01:19:20.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>On pense que ça aura</c>
<c.green.bg_black>un effet majeur</c>

01:19:20.600 --> 01:19:22.520 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>sur les aliments qu'on peut</c>

01:19:22.880 --> 01:19:24.560 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>tous trouver en supermarché.</c>

01:19:28.360 --> 01:19:31.160 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-Comment voulez-vous que ceux</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui ont les financements</c>

01:19:31.520 --> 01:19:34.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>et les structures</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de recherche et développement</c>

01:19:34.720 --> 01:19:37.360 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>s'engagent à faire vraiment</c>
<c.green.bg_black>changer les choses</c>

01:19:37.560 --> 01:19:39.320 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>si vous n'êtes pas à leurs côtés ?</c>

01:19:40.560 --> 01:19:42.240 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Je m'appelle Derek Yach.</c>

01:19:42.960 --> 01:19:47.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai fait des études de médecine</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et épidémiologie en Afrique du Sud.</c>

01:19:47.400 --> 01:19:49.320 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai été le 1er Sud-Africain</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à rejoindre</c>

01:19:49.520 --> 01:19:53.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>l'Organisation mondiale de la Santé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>après la fin de l'apartheid.</c>

01:19:53.480 --> 01:19:55.960 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'y suis allé pour un an</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et y suis resté dix.</c>

01:19:56.760 --> 01:19:59.920 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>J'ai dirigé des travaux</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur les maladies chroniques.</c>

01:20:01.080 --> 01:20:02.760 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>PepsiCo m'a contacté au moment</c>

01:20:03.120 --> 01:20:06.120 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>où Indra Nooyi est devenue</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la nouvelle PDG du groupe.</c>

01:20:06.480 --> 01:20:07.640 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Son discours était :</c>

01:20:07.840 --> 01:20:10.520 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>"Vous critiquez,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>mais on veut changer les choses.</c>

01:20:10.880 --> 01:20:12.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Donc, rejoignez-nous."</c>

01:20:15.040 --> 01:20:15.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Elle a ajouté :</c>

01:20:16.200 --> 01:20:18.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>"On a 2 milliards</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de consommateurs par jour.</c>

01:20:18.600 --> 01:20:20.720 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>S'ils mangent moins</c>
<c.green.bg_black>salé, sucré et gras,</c>

01:20:20.920 --> 01:20:23.200 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ça aura un impact important</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sur leur santé."</c>

01:20:23.400 --> 01:20:24.760 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Et l'idée m'a plu.</c>

01:20:26.280 --> 01:20:28.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Certains collègues</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de santé publique ont pensé</c>

01:20:28.960 --> 01:20:30.640 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>que j'étais passé à l'ennemi.</c>

01:20:31.320 --> 01:20:33.800 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Des efforts ont été faits</c>
<c.green.bg_black>pour rendre plus sains</c>

01:20:34.160 --> 01:20:35.360 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de nombreux produits.</c>

01:20:36.480 --> 01:20:38.320 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Quand j'étais en poste,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>on a décidé</c>

01:20:38.520 --> 01:20:40.960 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de réduire</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la teneur en sucre des sodas.</c>

01:20:42.200 --> 01:20:44.440 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Le directeur marketing</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de l'époque a déclaré</c>

01:20:44.640 --> 01:20:46.280 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>que c'était</c>
<c.green.bg_black>du suicide commercial</c>

01:20:46.480 --> 01:20:48.800 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et que Coca allait rafler</c>
<c.green.bg_black>nos parts de marché.</c>

01:20:49.600 --> 01:20:52.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>En plus, il faut tenir compte</c>
<c.green.bg_black>des actionnaires.</c>

01:20:54.720 --> 01:20:55.720 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Indra a été soumise</c>

01:20:56.080 --> 01:20:59.000 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>à des pressions des investisseurs</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui disaient :</c>

01:20:59.200 --> 01:21:01.200 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>"Tenez-vous-en</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à ce que vous savez faire.</c>

01:21:01.400 --> 01:21:03.720 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Vous êtes une entreprise</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de sodas et d'encas,</c>

01:21:04.080 --> 01:21:07.600 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>vendez-les et ne vous souciez pas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de santé et d'environnement,</c>

01:21:07.960 --> 01:21:09.720 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>ça va nous coûter plus cher.</c>

01:21:09.920 --> 01:21:13.400 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>En tant qu'actionnaires, nous</c>
<c.green.bg_black>devrons financer ces recherches."</c>

01:21:16.880 --> 01:21:18.160 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Le prix de la majorité</c>

01:21:18.520 --> 01:21:22.280 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>des ingrédients sains</c>
<c.green.bg_black>composant notre alimentation</c>

01:21:22.480 --> 01:21:25.240 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>est beaucoup plus élevé</c>
<c.green.bg_black>que celui des produits de base</c>

01:21:25.600 --> 01:21:27.520 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>comme le riz, le blé,</c>

01:21:28.960 --> 01:21:32.760 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>le maïs ou le soja,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qui sont fortement subventionnés.</c>

01:21:34.960 --> 01:21:36.000 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ce n'est pas étonnant</c>

01:21:36.360 --> 01:21:39.240 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>que les entreprises choisissent</c>
<c.green.bg_black>l'option la moins chère.</c>

01:21:39.600 --> 01:21:43.840 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Fruits, légumes, noix et fruits secs</c>
<c.green.bg_black>coûtent beaucoup plus cher,</c>

01:21:44.200 --> 01:21:47.040 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>car ils sont non subventionnés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>dans la plupart des pays.</c>

01:21:47.240 --> 01:21:48.920 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>On n'en parle pas assez.</c>

01:21:49.120 --> 01:21:50.280 line:91% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>Ce facteur empêche</c>

01:21:50.640 --> 01:21:53.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>l'introduction</c>
<c.green.bg_black>de plus d'ingrédients sains</c>

01:21:53.240 --> 01:21:54.840 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>comme les fruits et les légumes.</c>

01:22:01.000 --> 01:22:02.680 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-La principale recommandation</c>

01:22:03.040 --> 01:22:04.880 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>de la classification NOVA</c>

01:22:05.240 --> 01:22:08.520 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>est qu'un régime sain</c>
<c.green.bg_black>doit se baser sur de vrais aliments</c>

01:22:08.880 --> 01:22:10.800 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>et des repas</c>
<c.green.bg_black>qu'on prépare soi-même,</c>

01:22:11.000 --> 01:22:13.160 line:83% align:left
<c.green.bg_black>pas sur des aliments</c>
<c.green.bg_black>ultratransformés.</c>

01:22:15.040 --> 01:22:17.040 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-La solution</c>
<c.green.bg_black>est relativement simple :</c>

01:22:18.400 --> 01:22:21.920 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>cuisiner autant que possible</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à partir d'ingrédients naturels.</c>

01:22:23.000 --> 01:22:24.600 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>Il n'y a que ça de vrai.</c>

01:22:28.280 --> 01:22:30.880 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>-Pour l'industrie,</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>elle doit continuer à croître.</c>

01:22:31.240 --> 01:22:32.760 line:91% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>La croissance est importante.</c>

01:22:32.960 --> 01:22:34.760 line:91% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>Du coup, elle va nous pousser</c>

01:22:35.120 --> 01:22:37.840 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>à manger souvent,</c>
<c.white.bg_black>à toutes les occasions,</c>

01:22:38.040 --> 01:22:42.000 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>ou aller vers des pays où les gens</c>
<c.white.bg_black>ne consomment pas encore beaucoup</c>

01:22:42.360 --> 01:22:45.520 line:83% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>et les pousser à consommer</c>
<c.yellow.bg_black>plus d'aliments ultratransformés,</c>

01:22:45.880 --> 01:22:47.320 line:91% align:center
<c.yellow.bg_black>ce qui est très profitable.</c>

01:22:48.280 --> 01:22:50.280 line:91% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>-En 1980, personne n'aurait prédit</c>

01:22:50.640 --> 01:22:53.400 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>qu'on serait</c>
<c.green.bg_black>en moins bonne santé en 2020.</c>

01:22:57.000 --> 01:22:59.520 line:83% align:center
<c.green.bg_black>Les produits ultratransformés</c>
<c.green.bg_black>sont associés</c>

01:22:59.880 --> 01:23:00.960 line:91% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>au diabète de type 2,</c>

01:23:01.160 --> 01:23:04.400 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>aux maladies cardiovasculaires,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>à la démence,</c>

01:23:04.760 --> 01:23:07.760 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>l'anxiété, la dépression,</c>
<c.green.bg_black>la prise de poids, l'obésité,</c>

01:23:07.960 --> 01:23:09.520 line:83% align:right
<c.green.bg_black>aux cancers</c>
<c.green.bg_black>et décès prématurés.</c>

01:23:11.560 --> 01:23:14.160 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>-Il n'y a pas d'intérêt réel</c>
<c.white.bg_black>pour le consommateur,</c>

01:23:14.360 --> 01:23:16.000 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>seulement des risques</c>
<c.white.bg_black>pour la santé.</c>

01:23:16.200 --> 01:23:17.360 line:91% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>On doit se demander :</c>

01:23:17.560 --> 01:23:20.800 line:83% align:left
<c.white.bg_black>doit-on prendre ces risques ?</c>
<c.white.bg_black>En valent-ils la peine ?</c>

01:23:21.160 --> 01:23:24.040 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>Musique ésotérique</c>

01:23:24.240 --> 01:25:29.800 line:91% align:center
<c.magenta.bg_black>...</c>

01:25:30.000 --> 01:25:33.000 line:83% align:center
<c.white.bg_black>Sous-titrage :</c>
<c.white.bg_black>Boulevard des Productions</c>

